in error message to user when the plan cannot be found in app view.","Errors_PlanGenericErrorBody":"Something went wrong. Please try again later.","_Errors_PlanGenericErrorBody.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-Errors] Body text for when a plan fails to open","Errors_PlanGenericErrorText":"We couldn\'t open your plan","_Errors_PlanGenericErrorText.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-Errors] Main text for when a plan fails to open (used by UNO/BasicPlanPage)","Errors_EvoPlanGenericErrorText":"Couldn\'t open your plan","_Errors_EvoPlanGenericErrorText.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-Errors] Main text for when a plan fails to open (EVO-specific version)","Errors_PlanGoToMyPlansButtonText":"Go to My plans","_Errors_PlanGoToMyPlansButtonText.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-Errors] Button text for button to navigate to my plans page when in the error view","Errors_PlanGoBackToPlansButtonText":"Open My plans","_Errors_PlanGoBackToPlansButtonText.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-Errors] Button text for button to navigate to my plans page when in the error view","Errors_PlanInaccessibleErrorText":"You do not have access","_Errors_PlanInaccessibleErrorText.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-Errors] Main text for when a user no longer has access to a plan","Errors_PlanInaccessibleErrorBody":"Contact the owner to request access.","_Errors_PlanInaccessibleErrorBody.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-Errors] Body text for when a user no longer has access to a plan","Errors_EvoPlanInaccessibleErrorBody":"Ask the owner to add you to this plan.","Errors_EvoPlanInaccessibleErrorBody.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-Errors] Body text for when a user no longer has access to a Evo plan","Errors_PlanNotFoundErrorText":"This plan has been deleted","_Errors_PlanNotFoundErrorText.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-Errors] Main text for the not found error view","Errors_PlanNotFoundErrorBody":"Now that it can\'t be used anymore, you can remove it from showing up in your list of recently used plans.","_Errors_PlanNotFoundErrorBody.comment":"[TA