ons_OpenInBrowser.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-FileSuggestionsContextMenu] Message for the open in browser option for a file suggestion","FileSuggestions_OpenInDesktopApp":"Open in desktop app","_FileSuggestions_OpenInDesktopApp.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-FileSuggestionsContextMenu] Message for the open in desktop app option for a file suggestion","FileSuggestions_CopyLink":"Copy link","_FileSuggestions_CopyLink.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-FileSuggestionsContextMenu] Message for the copy link action for a file suggestion","FileSuggestions_AddAttachmentAriaLabel":"Add as attachment","_FileSuggestions_AddAttachmentAriaLabel.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-FileSuggestions] Aria label for the button to add a recommended file as an attachment.","FileSuggestions_AddAsAttachment":"Add","_FileSuggestions_AddAsAttachment.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-FileSuggestions] Button to add a given file suggestion as an attachment to the task","FileSuggestions_FileUsageText":"{0} by {1} on {2}","_FileSuggestions_FileUsageText.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-FileSuggestions] File usage text for a given file. {0} will be replaced by the usage type (created, last modified, last shared), {1} will be the user\'s name, and {2} will be the date string","FileSuggestions_Created":"Created","_FileSuggestions_Created.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-FileSuggestions] Text shown to the user when file blurbs are shown from the creation info. See FileUsageText entry 0","FileSuggestions_LastModified":"Last modified","_FileSuggestions_LastModified.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-FileSuggestions] Text shown to the user when file blurbs are shown from the last modified info. See FileUsageText entry 0","FileSuggestions_LastShared":"Last shared","_FileSuggestions_LastShared.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-FileSuggestions] Text shown to the user when file blurbs are shown from the last shared info. See FileUsageText entry 0","FileSuggestions_UnknownUser":"unknown user","_FileSuggestions_UnknownUser.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-FileSuggestions] Text shown in FileUsageText if the user isn\'t known","FileSuggestions_UnknownDate":"unknown date","_FileSuggestions_UnknownDate.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-FileSuggestions] Text shown in FileUsageText if the date isn\'t known","FileSuggestions_FileSuggestionsCardAriaLabel":", Use left and right arrow keys to access important file suggestion actions.","_FileSuggestions_FileSuggestionsCardAriaLabel.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Todoweb-Shared] Accessibility text for the task card.","FileSuggestions_Header":"Suggested attachments","_FileSuggestions_Header.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-FileSuggestions] The header for the file suggestions section","FileSuggestions_Subheader":"We\'ve included content we think might be associated with this task. You can only see content you have access to. Suggestions should become more relevant over time.","_FileSuggestions_Subheader.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-FileSuggestions] The subheader for the file suggestions section","FileSuggestions_SeeMore":"See more","_FileSuggestions_SeeMore.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-FileSuggestions] Button to see more file suggestions","FileSuggestions_SeeLess":"See less","_FileSuggestions_SeeLess.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-FileSuggestions] Button to see fewer file suggestions","FileSuggestions_SeeMoreAriaLabel":"See more file suggestions","_FileSuggestions_SeeMoreAriaLabel.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-FileSuggestions] Aria label for the button to see more file suggestions","FileSuggestions_SeeLessAriaLabel":"See fewer file suggestions","_FileSuggestions_SeeLessAriaLabel.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-FileSuggestions] Aria label for the button to see fewer file suggestions","FileSuggestions_NoSuggestedFiles":"No Suggested files","_FileSuggestions_NoSuggestedFiles.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-FileSuggestions] Text shown to the user when there were no suggested files","GroupCreation_GroupCreationDisabledHeader":"Plan and Microsoft 365 Group Creation Disabled","_GroupCreation_GroupCreationDisabledHeader.comment":"{PlaceHolder=\\"Microsoft 365\\"}[BRANDING][TAG:APPS-Todoweb-Error-GroupCreationDisabled]Error dialog\'s header used when group creation is disallowed for current user.","GroupCreation_GroupCreationDisabledMessage":"Your organization\'s global admin has turned off the ability to create or copy new Plans and Microsoft 365 Groups.","_GroupCreation_GroupCreationDisabledMessage.comment":"{PlaceHolder=\\"Microsoft 365\\"}[BRANDING][TAG:APPS-Todoweb-Error-GroupCreationDisabled]Error dialog\'s description used when group creation is disallowed for current user.","GroupCreation_PlanCreationDisabledMessage":"You are not a member of an existing group. To create a new Microsoft 365 Group, contact your organization\'s global admin.","_GroupCreation_PlanCreationDisabledMessage.comment":"{PlaceHolder=\\"Microsoft 365\\"}[BRANDING][TAG:APPS-Todoweb-Error-GroupCreationDisabled]Error dialog\'s description used when, on top of group creation disallowed, current user doesn\'t belong to any existing group.","GroupSettings_GroupDescriptionLabel":"Group description","_GroupSettings_GroupDescriptionLabel.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-GroupSettings]Label for the edit group description text area","GroupSettings_VisibilityMode_Public":"Public - Anyone in my organization can see plan contents","_GroupSettings_VisibilityMode_Public.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-GroupSettings]Option text for the visibility level selection. This level means that the plan will be visible to everyone in the organization","GroupSettings_VisibilityMode_Private":"Private - Only members I add can see plan contents","_GroupSettings_VisibilityMode_Private.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-GroupSettings]Option text for the visibility level selection. This level means that the plan will only be visible to the members inside the plan.","GroupSettings_ClassificationDescriptionHeader":"Classification allows our organization to protect data based on our policies and standards.","_GroupSettings_ClassificationDescriptionHeader.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-GroupSettings]Header of helper text for classification description. This is shown when user hovers on the info icon.","GroupSettings_ClassificationUsageGuidelinesURL":"Usage guidelines","_GroupSettings_ClassificationUsageGuidelinesURL.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-GroupSettings]The text shown to user that links to usage guidelines website.","GroupSettings_DeleteGroup":"Delete this group","_GroupSettings_DeleteGroup.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-GroupSettings]Text for the delete group button","GroupSettings_NameError_Empty":"The group name must contain at least one character.","_GroupSettings_NameError_Empty.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Todoweb-GroupSettings]Error text for empty group name. This is checked locally.","GroupSettings_NameError_Blocked":"The group name contains blocked words that do not meet company policy.","_GroupSettings_NameError_Blocked.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Todoweb-GroupSettings]Error text for group name that matches the list of blocked words. It could be Microsoft defined, tenant admin defined, or default reserved words.","GroupSettings_NameError_MissingPrefixSuffix":"The group name is missing an organization required prefix or suffix. Sample name: {0}Group Name{1}","_GroupSettings_NameError_MissingPrefixSuffix.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Todoweb-GroupSettings]Error text for group name that\'s missing organization required prefix or suffix. At runtime, {0} will be replaced with required prefix string and {1} will be replaced with suffix.","GroupSettings_NameError_Unknown":"The group name failed validation. Try another name.","_GroupSettings_NameError_Unknown.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Todoweb-GroupSettings]Default error text for group name validation.","LabelEditor_EditLabel":"Edit label","_LabelEditor_EditLabel.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-LabelEditor] Label text describing the label editor callout","LabelEditor_EditLabelNameAriaLabel":"Edit label name","_LabelEditor_EditLabelNameAriaLabel.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-LabelEditor] aria label text describing the label name edit field","LabelPicker_NoResultsFound":"No results found","_LabelPicker_NoResultsFound.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-LabelPicker] Shown when no labels are found with a particular keyword","LabelPicker_AddLabel":"Add label","_LabelPicker_AddLabel.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-LabelPicker] Shown when no labels are applied to task","LabelPicker_AllLabelsAdded":"All labels added","_LabelPicker_AllLabelsAdded.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-LabelPicker] Shown when no labels are found with a particular keyword because all the labels have been added","LabelPicker_SearchForLabel":"Search for label","_LabelPicker_SearchForLabel.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-LabelPicker] Placeholder text shown in the label picker until text is entered","LabelPicker_SearchForLabelAriaLabel":"Search for label to apply to the task","_LabelPicker_SearchForLabelAriaLabel.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-LabelPicker] Aria label text in the label picker until text is entered","LabelPicker_SearchResultCountSingular":"1 result found","_LabelPicker_SearchResultCountSingular.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-LabelPicker] Announcement text when exactly one result is found in the label picker.","LabelPicker_SearchResultCountPlural":"{0} results found","_LabelPicker_SearchResultCountPlural.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-LabelPicker] Announcement text when results are searched declaring the number of suggestions returned. {0} will be replaced with the label count.","LabelPicker_SuggestionAriaLabel":"{0}, selected. Press enter to add this label, press right arrow to edit label name","_LabelPicker_SuggestionAriaLabel.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-LabelPicker] Aria label for label suggestions in the floating picker. Includes keyboard instructions for screen reader users. {0} will be replaced with the label name.","Labels_UnlabeledText":"No label","_Labels_UnlabeledText.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-Labels] String for the set of tasks that haven\'t had a label applied","Labels_PinkLabelPlaceholderText":"Pink","_Labels_P