olor.","Labels_SilverLabelPlaceholderText":"Silver","_Labels_SilverLabelPlaceholderText.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-Labels] Text to show in the label display if the silver label hasn\'t been given a name. \'Silver\' describes a gray color.","Labels_BrownLabelPlaceholderText":"Brown","_Labels_BrownLabelPlaceholderText.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-Labels] Text to show in the label display if the brown label hasn\'t been given a name.","Labels_CranberryLabelPlaceholderText":"Cranberry","_Labels_CranberryLabelPlaceholderText.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-Labels] Text to show in the label display if the cranberry label hasn\'t been given a name. \'Cranberry\' describes a maroon red color.","Labels_OrangeLabelPlaceholderText":"Orange","_Labels_OrangeLabelPlaceholderText.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-Labels] Text to show in the label display if the orange label hasn\'t been given a name. \'Orange\' describes the color.","Labels_PeachLabelPlaceholderText":"Peach","_Labels_PeachLabelPlaceholderText.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-Labels] Text to show in the label display if the peach label hasn\'t been given a name. \'Peach\' describes a bright orange color.","Labels_MarigoldLabelPlaceholderText":"Marigold","_Labels_MarigoldLabelPlaceholderText.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-Labels] Text to show in the label display if the marigold label hasn\'t been given a name. \'Marigold\' describes a yellow-orange color.","Labels_LightGreenLabelPlaceholderText":"Light green","_Labels_LightGreenLabelPlaceholderText.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-Labels] Text to show in the label display if the light green label hasn\'t been given a name.","Labels_DarkGreenLabelPlaceholderText":"Dark green","_Labels_DarkGreenLabelPlaceholderText.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-Labels] Text to show in the label display if the dark green label hasn\'t been given a name.","Labels_TealLabelPlaceholderText":"Teal","_Labels_TealLabelPlaceholderText.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-Labels] Text to show in the label display if the teal 