ls in the plan","LeftNav_SwitchViewTasks":"My Tasks & Plans","_LeftNav_SwitchViewTasks.comment":"Tasks option in the left nav switch view dropdown","LeftNav_SwitchViewPublishing":"Publishing","_LeftNav_SwitchViewPublishing.comment":"Publishing option in the left nav switch view dropdown","LeftNav_DropdownTasksViewOption":"My tasks and plans","_LeftNav_DropdownTasksViewOption.comment":"[TAG:APPS-LeftNav] Dropdown option to switch to personal tasks page.","Loop_RenderError":"Failed to load Loop page","_Loop_RenderError.comment":"{PlaceHolder=\\"Loop\\"}[BRANDING][TAG:APPS-Planner-Error] Error message displayed when rendering a Loop component fails.","Loop_RenderErrorSubtext":"Please try again in a while.","_Loop_RenderErrorSubtext.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-Error] Supporting message for the error displayed when rendering a Loop component fails.","Loop_GenericRenderError":"Something went wrong","_Loop_GenericRenderError.comment":"{\\"Ambiguity\\":{\\"wrong\\":\\"not functioning correctly\\"}} [TAG:APPS-Planner-Error] Error message displayed when rendering a Loop component fails with generic error.","Loop_GenericRenderErrorSubtext":"Please try opening this again in some time","_Loop_GenericRenderErrorSubtext.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-Error] Supporting message for the error displayed when rendering a Loop component fails with generic error.","Loop_OfflineRenderError":"No internet connection","_Loop_OfflineRenderError.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-Error] Error message displayed when rendering a Loop component fails with offline error.","Loop_OfflineRenderErrorSubtext":"Please check your network connection and try again","_Loop_OfflineRenderErrorSubtext.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-Error] Supporting message for the error displayed when rendering a Loop component fails with offline error.","Loop_FileNotFoundOrAccessDeniedError_ItemNotFoundRenderError":"File not found","_Loop_FileNotFoundOrAccessDeniedError_ItemNotFoundRenderError.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-Error] Error message displayed when rendering a Loop component fails with file not found error.","Loop_FileNotFoundOrAccessDeniedError_ItemNotFoundRenderErrorSubtext":"It looks like this file may have been deleted.","_Loop_FileNotFoundOrAccessDeniedError_ItemNotFoundRenderErrorSubtext.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-Error] Supporting message for the error displayed when rendering a Loop component fails with file not found error.","Loop_AuthorizationError_AccessDeniedRenderError":"Access denied","_Loop_AuthorizationError_AccessDeniedRenderError.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-Error] Error message displayed when rendering a Loop component fails with access denied authorization error.","Loop_AuthorizationError_AccessDeniedRenderErrorSubtext":"You do not have the required permissions to view this file. Please contact your admin to change the settings","_Loop_AuthorizationError_AccessDeniedRenderErrorSubtext.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-Error] Supporting message for the error displayed when rendering a Loop component fails with access denied authorization error.","Loop_AuthorizationError_AuthChallengeRequiredRenderError":"You are not connected to CorpNet","_Loop_AuthorizationError_AuthChallengeRequiredRenderError.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-Error] Error message displayed when rendering a Loop component fails with auth challenge required authorization error. This specially happens when users are not connected to their CorpNet that means corporate network.","Loop_AuthorizationError_AuthChallengeRequiredRenderErrorSubtext":"Please connect to your corporate network to view the content or contact your admin to change the settings.","_Loop_AuthorizationError_AuthChallengeRequiredRenderErrorSubtext.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-Error] Supporting message for the error displayed when rendering a Loop component fails with auth challenged required authorization error.","Loop_FileContentAccessDeniedRenderErrorEVO":"Couldn\'t open this page","_Loop_FileContentAccessDeniedRenderErrorEVO.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-Error] Error message displayed when rendering a Loop component fails with content access denied error.","Loop_FileContentAccessDeniedRenderErrorSubtextEVO":"Open this Loop page in a browser or update the plan\'s sensitivity label to \\"{0}\\".","_Loop_FileContentAccessDeniedRenderErrorSubtextEVO.comment":"{PlaceHolder=\\"Loop\\"}[BRANDING][TAG:APPS-Planner-Error] Supporting message for the error displayed when rendering a Loop component fails with content access denied error. {0} will be replaced with the sensitivity label name.","Loop_FileContentAccessDeniedRenderError":"This content is protected","_Loop_FileContentAccessDeniedRenderError.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-Error] Error message displayed when rendering a Loop component fails with content access denied error.","Loop_FileContentAccessDeniedRenderErrorSubtext":"This Loop file includes content protected by a sensitivity label. Ask the plan owner or your organization\'s admin for access.","_Loop_FileContentAccessDeniedRenderErrorSubtext.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-Error] Supporting message for the error displayed when rendering a Loop component fails with content access denied error.","Loop_AccessDenied_OpenInBrowserButton":"Open in browser","_Loop_AccessDenied_OpenInBrowserButton.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-Error] Button text shown on the access denied error view to open the Loop file in the browser.","Loop_AccessDenied_LearnHowLink":"Learn how.","_Loop_AccessDenied_LearnHowLink.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-Error] Link text shown on the access denied error view to learn how to update sensitivity labels.","Notifications_AddUsersToGroupError":"We couldn\'t add \\"{0}\\" users to the plan.","_Notifications_AddUsersToGroupError.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-Error] Error message seen when adding users to the group fails. {0} will be replaced by the number of users","Notifications_JoinUnifiedGroupError":"Unable to join. We ran into an issue and were not able to add you to the plan. Try again later.","_Notifications_JoinUnifiedGroupError.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-Error] Error message seen when joining the group fails. The first sentence is in bold text","Notifications_BasicLimitsError":"We couldn\'t complete your request because your item or storage limit has been exceeded.","_Notifications_BasicLimitsError.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-Error]text for when user hits basic limits error","Notifications_CopyPlanError":"We couldn\'t copy your plan. Please try again later.","_Notifications_CopyPlanError.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-Error] Error message displayed when failed to copy a plan.","Notifications_CreateBucketError":"We couldn\'t create bucket \\"{0}\\". Please try again later.","_Notifications_CreateBucketError.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-Error] Error message displayed when creating a bucket fails. {0} will be replaced with the bucket name","Notifications_CreateGroupError":"We couldn\'t create this Microsoft 365 Group. Please try again later.","_Notifications_CreateGroupError.comment":"{PlaceHolder=\\"Microsoft 365\\"}[BRANDING][TAG:APPS-Planner-Error] Error message displayed when failed to create a new group.","Notifications_CreatePlanError":"We couldn\'t create your plan \\"{0}\\". Please try again later.","_Notifications_CreatePlanError.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-Error] Error message displayed when failed to create a new plan. {0} will be replaced with the plan name","Notifications_CreateTaskError":"We couldn\'t create task \\"{0}\\". Please try again later.","_Notifications_CreateTaskError.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-Error] Error message displayed when creating a task fails. {0} will be replaced with the task name","Notifications_DeleteBucketError":"We couldn\'t delete bucket \\"{0}\\". Please try again later.","_Notifications_DeleteBucketError.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-Error] Error message displayed when deleting a bucket fails. {0} will be replaced with the bucket name","Notifications_DeleteBucketErrorWithUpdateConflict":"We couldn\'t delete bucket \\"{0}\\". It has been updated by another user.","_Notifications_DeleteBucketErrorWithUpdateConflict.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-Error] Error String seen when deleting a bucket fails because it has updates the current user doesn\'t know about. {0} will be replaced with bucket title.","Notifications_DeletePlanError":"We couldn\'t delete plan \\"{0}\\". Please try again later.","_Notifications_DeletePlanError.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-Error] Error message displayed when deleting a plan fails. {0} will be replaced with the plan name","Notifications_DeleteRecurringTaskSeriesDeleteError":"We couldn\'t delete task \\"{0}\\". Please try again later.","_Notifications_DeleteRecurringTaskSeriesDeleteError.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-Error] Error message displayed when deleting a recurring task series fails on delete. {0} will be replaced with the task name","Notifications_DeleteRecurringTaskSeriesUpdateError":"Recurrence for this task \\"{0}\\" was deleted, but we couldn\'t delete the task. Please try again later.","_Notifications_DeleteRecurringTaskSeriesUpdateError.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-Error] Error message displayed when deleting a recurring task series fails on update. {0} will be replaced with the task name","Notifications_DeleteTaskError":"We couldn\'t delete task \\"{0}\\". Please try again later.","_Notifications_DeleteTaskError.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-Error] Error message displayed when deleting a task fails. {0} will be replaced with the task name","Notifications_DeleteTaskErrorWithUpdateConflict":"We couldn\'t delete task \\"{0}\\". It has been updated by another user.","_Notifications_DeleteTaskErrorWithUpdateConflict.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-Error] Error String seen when deleting a task fails because it has updates the current user doesn\'t know about. {0} will be replaced with task title.","Notifications_DeleteTaskInGroupError":"Only members of the Microsoft 365 Group are allowed to delete tasks.","_Notifications_DeleteTaskInGroupError.comment":"{PlaceHolder=\\"Microsoft 365\\"}[BRANDING][TAG:APPS-Todoweb-Shared] Message for delete task auth failure in groups.","Notifications_ExportPlanError":"Sorry, we couldn\'t export your plan \\"{0}\\". Please try again later.","_Notifications_ExportPlanError.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-Error] Error message displayed when exporting plan fails. {0} will be replaced with the plan name","Notifications_UndeleteTaskError":"We couldn\'t restore task \\"{0}\\".","_Notifications_UndeleteTaskError.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-Error] Error message displayed when undeleting a task fails. {0} will be replaced with the task name","Notifications_GetPlanUsersError":"We couldn\'t load the users for this plan. Refresh now or try again later.","_Notifications_GetPlanUsersError.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-Error] Text shown on the error bar when failed to retrieve users of a plan.","Notifications_LoadingPlanDataError":"We couldn\'t load your plan. Please try again later.","_Notifications_LoadingPlanDataError.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-Error] Error String seen when loading the plan or its necessary sub entities for a plan level view","Notifications_FetchUserSettingsError":"We couldn\'t load your settings. Please try again later.","_Notifications_FetchUserSettingsError.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-Error] Error String seen when loading the user settings fails","Notifications_UpdateUserSettingsError":"We couldn\'t update your settings. Please try again later.","_Notifications_UpdateUserSettingsError.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-Error] Error String seen when updating the user settings fails","Notifications_GetPlansError":"We couldn\'t load your plans. Please try again later.","_Notifications_GetPlansError.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-Error] Error String seen when loading the list of plans fails","Notifications_GetJoinedGroupsError":"We couldn\'t load your groups. Please try again later.","_Notifications_GetJoinedGroupsError.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-Error] Error String seen when loading the list of user\'s joined groups fails","Notifications_GetTaskDetailsError":"We couldn\'t load details for task \\"{0}\\". Refresh now or try again later.","_Notifications_GetTaskDetailsError.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-Error] Error message seen when retrieving details for a task fails. {0} will be replaced with the task name","Notifications_DiffSyncMaxPlansSharedWithUserLimitError":"Please refresh the screen to see if other users have updated these tasks.","_Notifications_DiffSyncMaxPlansSharedWithUserLimitError.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-Info] Message shown when diff sync limit for the maximum number of projects that can be shared with a user is exceeded.","Notifications_UnknownTaskNotFoundError":"We couldn\'t load details for the given task. The task may have been deleted.","_Notifications_UnknownTaskNotFoundError.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-Error] Error message seen when trying to load a task but cannot find it since it should have been deleted.","Notifications_TaskNotFoundError":"We couldn\'t load details for task \\"{0}\\". The task may have been deleted.","_Notifications_TaskNotFoundError.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-Error] Error message seen when trying to load a task but cannot find it since it should have been deleted. {0} will be replaced with the task name","Notifications_GetTasksForPlanError":"We couldn\'t load tasks for \\"{0}\\". Please try again later.","_Notifications_GetTasksForPlanError.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-Error] Error message seen when getting tasks for a plan fails. {0} will be replaced with the plan name","Notifications_GetTasksForPlanNoTitleError":"We couldn\'t load tasks for your plan. Please try again later.","_Notifications_GetTasksForPlanNoTitleError.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-Error] Error message seen when getting tasks for a plan fails.","Notifications_GetTasksPageForPlanError":"We were unable to load all the tasks for this plan. Refresh the page to try again.","_Notifications_GetTasksPageForPlanError.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-Error] Error message seen when getting tasks for a plan fails partially (i.e we get some tasks but not all).","Notifications_GetTasksForUserError":"We couldn\'t load tasks for you. Please try again later.","_Notifications_GetTasksForUserError.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-Error] Error message seen when getting tasks for current user fails.","Notifications_GroupFetchError":"We couldn\'t load group information. Please try again later.","_Notifications_GroupFetchError.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-Error] Error String. Not able to fetch the group data","Notifications_LoadConversationsError":"We can\'t show comments right now. Check again in a few minutes.","_Notifications_LoadConversationsError.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-Error] Error string seen when can\'t load conversations for a task.","Notifications_PostGroupConversationThreadError":"We couldn\'t post your comment. Please try again later.","_Notifications_PostGroupConversationThreadError.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-Error] Error string seen when can\'t post a comment in a task.","Notifications_LoadPlanError":"We couldn\'t load the \\"{0}\\" plan. Please try again later.","_Notifications_LoadPlanError.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-Error] Error String seen when loading a plan fails. {0} will be replaced with the plan id","Notifications_MoveBasicPlanError":"We couldn\'t move your plan \\"{0}\\". Please try again later.","_Notifications_MoveBasicPlanError.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-Error] Error message displayed when failed to move a plan. {0} will be replaced with the plan title.","Notifications_MoveBasicTaskError":"We couldn\'t move your task \\"{0}\\". Please try again later.","_Notifications_MoveBasicTaskError.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-Error] Error message displayed when failed to move a task. {0} will be replaced with the task title.","Notifications_MoveBasicTaskNoTitleError":"We couldn\'t move your task. Please try again later.","_Notifications_MoveBasicTaskNoTitleError.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-Error] Error message displayed when failed to move a task.","Notifications_NetworkError":"You can\'t update plans or tasks when you\'re offline. Reconnect and try again.","_Notifications_NetworkError.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-Error] Error String seen when they lose internet connectivity","Notifications_NotificationBarAriaLabel":"Notification message bar","_Notifications_NotificationBarAriaLabel.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-Notification] Aria label for the notification bar where errors, warnings and info messages will be displayed","Notifications_NotificationBarDismissAriaLabel":"Clear notification","_Notifications_NotificationBarDismissAriaLabel.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-Notification] Aria label for the notification bar dismiss button, that will clear the current notification from the screen","Notifications_RemoveUserFromGroupError":"We couldn\'t remove \\"{0}\\" from the Microsoft 365 Group.","_Notifications_RemoveUserFromGroupError.comment":"{PlaceHolder=\\"Microsoft 365\\"}[BRANDING][TAG:APPS-Planner-Error] Error message seen when removing a user from the group fails. {0} will be replaced by the user name","NotificationBar_ServiceUnavailableError":"We couldn\'t complete your request because the service is temporarily unavailable. Please try again later.","_NotificationBar_ServiceUnavailableError.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-Error] Error String seen when the service is unavailable. This is a generic error message that can be used for any service unavailability.","Notifications_ServiceReadOnlyTryInAFewHours":"Sorry, we can\'t make changes to your plan right now. Please try again in a few hours.","_Notifications_ServiceReadOnlyTryInAFewHours.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-Error] String for readonly error, the service should be editable again in more than 1 hour.","Notifications_ServiceReadOnlyTryInAFewMinutes":"Sorry, we can\'t make changes to your plan right now. Please try again in a few minutes.","_Notifications_ServiceReadOnlyTryInAFewMinutes.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-Error] String for readonly error, 