oupError limit error","Notifications_MaxTasksAssignedToUserError":"This user has been assigned the maximum number of tasks. Complete, delete, or reassign one of their tasks to assign another.","_Notifications_MaxTasksAssignedToUserError.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-Error]text for when user hits MaxTasksAssignedToUserError limit error","Notifications_MaxTasksCreatedByUserError":"You have created the maximum number of tasks per user. Delete a task to create another.","_Notifications_MaxTasksCreatedByUserError.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-Error]text for when user hits MaxTasksCreatedByUserError limit error","Notifications_MaxAssigneesInTasksError":"You can assign a task to no more than 11 team members.","_Notifications_MaxAssigneesInTasksError.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-Error]text for when user hits MaxAssigneesInTasksError limit error","Notifications_MaxLinksOnTaskError":"You can have only 10 attachments. Remove one to attach another.","_Notifications_MaxLinksOnTaskError.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-Error]text for when user hits MaxLinksOnTaskError limit error","Notifications_MaxChecklistItemsOnTaskError":"You can have only 20 checklist items. Delete one to create another.","_Notifications_MaxChecklistItemsOnTaskError.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-Error]text for when user hits MaxChecklistItemsOnTaskError limit error","Notifications_MaxBucketsInPlanError":"Oops, you\'ve reached your bucket limit.","_Notifications_MaxBucketsInPlanError.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-Error]text for when user hits MaxBucketsInPlanError limit error","Notifications_MaxContextsOnPlanError":"We couldn\'t complete your request because your item or storage limit has been exceeded.","_Notifications_MaxContextsOnPlanError.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-Error]text for when user hits MaxContextsOnPlanError limit error","Notifications_MaxTasksInPlanError":"You have reached the maximum number of tasks for this plan. Delete a task to create another.","_Notifications_MaxTasksInPlanError.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Plan