ddApprover_ApprovalRequestSection_Pending":"Pending","_AddApprover_ApprovalRequestSection_Pending.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-ApprovalCard] The tag text for the approval request link title when approval is required and approval has been requested and waiting for approver.","AddApprover_ApprovalRequestSection_Approved":"Approved","_AddApprover_ApprovalRequestSection_Approved.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-ApprovalCard] The tag text for the approval request link title when approval has been approved.","AddApprover_ApprovalRequestSection_Retry":"Retry","_AddApprover_ApprovalRequestSection_Retry.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-ApprovalCard] Retry button when we get approval information but missing approval detail information, this may happens when diff sync is too fast so we allow user to retry.","AddApprover_ApprovalRequestSection_ApprovalDetailAPIErrorMessage":"We couldn\'t retrieve the approval details. Please retry or reload the Planner app.","_AddApprover_ApprovalRequestSection_ApprovalDetailAPIErrorMessage.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-ApprovalCard] The error message shown when the API to get approval detail got problem, this may happens when diff sync is too fast so we allow user to retry.","AddApprover_ApprovalRequestSection_RequestText_Requested":"{0} requested approval from {1} {2} at {3}. ","_AddApprover_ApprovalRequestSection_RequestText_Requested.comment":"The non-bolded request text shown when Approval Status is Requested. Fill Requester, Handler, RequestDate and RequestTime into {0}{1}{2}{3}","AddApprover_ApprovalRequestSection_RequestText_Other":"{0} requested approval {1} at {2}. ","_AddApprover_ApprovalRequestSection_RequestText_Other.comment":"The non-bolded request text shown when Approval Status is Approved, Rejected or Cancelled. Fill Requester, RequestDate and RequestTime into {0}{1}{2}","AddApprover_ApprovalRequestSection_ResultText_Approved":"{0} approved the request {1} at {2}.  ","_AddApprover_ApprovalRequestSection_ResultText_Approved.comment":"The bolded result text shown when Approval Status is Approved. Fill Handler, CompletionDate and CompletionTime into {0}{1}{2}","AddApprover_ApprovalRequestSection_ResultText_Rejected":"{0} rejected the request {1} at {2}.  ","_AddApprover_ApprovalRequestSection_ResultText_Rejected.comment":"The bolded result text shown when Approval Status is Rejected. Fill Handler, CompletionDate and CompletionTime into {0}{1}{2}","AddApprover_ApprovalRequestSection_ResultText_Cancelled":"The approval request from {0} was canceled on {1} at {2}. ","_AddApprover_ApprovalRequestSection_ResultText_Cancelled.comment":"The bolded result text shown when Approval Status is Cancelled. Fill Requester, RequestDate and RequestTime into {0}{1}{2}","AddApprover_ApprovalRequestSection_UnknownStatus_ErrorMessage":"Error: Got unknown status.","_AddApprover_ApprovalRequestSection_UnknownStatus_ErrorMessage.comment":"The error message when got unknown status of approval. This is for robust.","AddApprover_AddApproverLink_AddAnApprover":"Add an approver","_AddApprover_AddApproverLink_AddAnApprover.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-ApprovalCard] The link text of the approval request.","AddApprover_ApprovalCardDetail_StatusApprovalRequested":"Status: In progress","_AddApprover_ApprovalCardDetail_StatusApprovalRequested.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-ApprovalCard] The text of status shown on the top of the approval detail card when approval is pending.","AddApprover_ApprovalCardDetail_WaitingOn":"Waiting on","_AddApprover_ApprovalCardDetail_WaitingOn.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-ApprovalCard] The text of status shown inside the approval detail card in front of approver when approval is pending.","AddApprover_ApprovalCardDetail_FinalStatusApproved":"Final status: Approved","_AddApprover_ApprovalCardDetail_FinalStatusApproved.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-ApprovalCard] The text of status shown on the top of the approval detail card when approval has been made.","AddApprover_ApprovalCardDetail_ApprovedBy":"Approved by","_Add