ement":"Column moved to position {0}","_CanvasGrid_ColumnMovedAnnouncement.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-CanvasGrid] Screen reader announcement when a column is reordered. {0} is the new position","CanvasGrid_CopiedAnnouncement":"Copied {0}","_CanvasGrid_CopiedAnnouncement.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-CanvasGrid] Screen reader announcement when cells are copied. {0} is a description of what was copied","CanvasGrid_CutAnnouncement":"Cut {0}","_CanvasGrid_CutAnnouncement.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-CanvasGrid] Screen reader announcement when cells are cut. {0} is a description of what was cut","CanvasGrid_DeletedSingleRowAnnouncement":"Deleted 1 row","_CanvasGrid_DeletedSingleRowAnnouncement.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-CanvasGrid] Screen reader announcement when 1 row is deleted","CanvasGrid_DeletedMultipleRowsAnnouncement":"Deleted {0} rows","_CanvasGrid_DeletedMultipleRowsAnnouncement.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-CanvasGrid] Screen reader announcement when multiple rows are deleted. {0} is the number of rows","CanvasGrid_CellsClearedAnnouncement":"Cells cleared","_CanvasGrid_CellsClearedAnnouncement.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-CanvasGrid] Screen reader announcement when cell values are cleared","CanvasGrid_ToggledAnnouncement":"Toggled","_CanvasGrid_ToggledAnnouncement.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-CanvasGrid] Screen reader announcement when a cell is toggled (e.g., checkbox)","CanvasGrid_EditingAnnouncement":"Editing {0}","_CanvasGrid_EditingAnnouncement.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-CanvasGrid] Screen reader announcement when entering edit mode. {0} is the column name or \'cell\' if unknown","CanvasGrid_EditingCellFallback":"cell","_CanvasGrid_EditingCellFallback.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-CanvasGrid] Fallback text for editing announcement when column name is unknown","CanvasGrid_CollapsedAnnouncement":"Collapsed","_CanvasGrid_CollapsedAnnouncement.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-CanvasGrid] Screen reader announcement when a tree row is collapsed","CanvasGrid_ExpandedAnnouncement":"Expanded","_CanvasGrid_ExpandedAnnouncement.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-CanvasGrid] Screen reader announcement when a tree row is expanded","CanvasGrid_InsertRowAboveAnnouncement":"Inserted row above","_CanvasGrid_InsertRowAboveAnnouncement.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-CanvasGrid] Screen reader announcement when a row is inserted above the current row via Shift+Enter","CanvasGrid_NewRowFallback":"New row","_CanvasGrid_NewRowFallback.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-CanvasGrid] Fallback screen reader announcement when footer row is activated and no label is provided","CanvasGrid_DragToReorderTooltip":"Drag to reorder","_CanvasGrid_DragToReorderTooltip.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-CanvasGrid] Tooltip shown when hovering over the row drag handle","CanvasGrid_InsertRowTooltip":"Insert row","_CanvasGrid_InsertRowTooltip.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-CanvasGrid] Tooltip shown when hovering over the insert row button","CanvasGrid_DragToFillTooltip":"Drag to fill","_CanvasGrid_DragToFillTooltip.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-CanvasGrid] Tooltip shown when hovering over the fill handle","CanvasGrid_ClipboardSelectionFallback":"selection","_CanvasGrid_ClipboardSelectionFallback.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-CanvasGrid] Fallback text for clipboard operation when no selection state is available","CanvasGrid_ClipboardSingleRow":"1 row","_CanvasGrid_ClipboardSingleRow.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-CanvasGrid] Description for clipboard operation affecting 1 row","CanvasGrid_ClipboardMultipleRows":"{0} rows","_CanvasGrid_ClipboardMultipleRows.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-CanvasGrid] Description for clipboard operation affecting multiple rows. {0} is the number of rows","CanvasGrid_ClipboardSingleCell":"cell","_CanvasGrid_ClipboardSingleCell.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-CanvasGrid] Description for clipboard operation affecting a single cell","CanvasGrid_ClipboardSingleCellWithColumn":"cell: {0}","_CanvasGrid_ClipboardSingleCellWithColumn.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-CanvasGrid] Description for clipboard operation affecting a single cell with column name. {0} is the column name","CanvasGrid_ClipboardCellsWithColumns":"{0} × {1} cells: {2}","_CanvasGrid_ClipboardCellsWithColumns.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-CanvasGrid] Description for clipboard operation with column names. {0} is row count, {1} is column count, {2} is column names","CanvasGrid_ClipboardCells":"{0} × {1} cells","_CanvasGrid_ClipboardCells.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-CanvasGrid] Description for clipboard operation without column names. {0} is row count, {1} is column count","CanvasTaskGrid_ClipboardBooleanYes":"Yes","_CanvasTaskGrid_ClipboardBooleanYes.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-CanvasTaskGrid] Text for boolean \'true\' value when copied to clipboard","CanvasTaskGrid_ClipboardBooleanNo":"No","_CanvasTaskGrid_ClipboardBooleanNo.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-CanvasTaskGrid] Text for boolean \'false\' value when copied to clipboard","CanvasTaskGrid_CellEmptyValue":"empty","_CanvasTaskGrid_CellEmptyValue.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-CanvasTaskGrid] Screen reader text for empty cell values","CanvasTaskGrid_EditCancelledAnnouncement":"Edit cancelled","_CanvasTaskGrid_EditCancelledAnnouncement.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-CanvasTaskGrid] Screen reader announcement when edit is cancelled","CanvasTaskGrid_MovingTasksPreview":"Moving {0} tasks","_CanvasTaskGrid_MovingTasksPreview.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-CanvasTaskGrid] Drag preview tooltip when moving multiple tasks. {0} is the number of tasks","CanvasTaskGrid_SwitchToDragMode":"Switch to drag mode","_CanvasTaskGrid_SwitchToDragMode.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-CanvasTaskGrid] Tooltip and aria-label for switching from selection mode to drag mode","CanvasTaskGrid_SwitchToSelectionMode":"Switch to selection mode","_CanvasTaskGrid_SwitchToSelectionMode.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-CanvasTaskGrid] Tooltip and aria-label for switching from drag mode to selection mode","CanvasTaskGrid_ColumnAddedAnnouncement":"{0} added","_CanvasTaskGrid_ColumnAddedAnnouncement.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-CanvasTaskGrid] Screen reader announcement when a column is added. {0} is the column name","CanvasTaskGrid_ColumnHiddenAnnouncement":"Column {0} hidden","_CanvasTaskGrid_ColumnHiddenAnnouncement.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-CanvasTaskGrid] Screen reader announcement when a column is hidden. {0} is the column name","CanvasTaskGrid_AllRowsExpandedAnnouncement":"All rows expanded","_CanvasTaskGrid_AllRowsExpandedAnnouncement.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-CanvasTaskGrid] Screen reader announcement when all rows are expanded","CanvasTaskGrid_AllRowsCollapsedAnnouncement":"All rows collapsed","_CanvasTaskGrid_AllRowsCollapsedAnnouncement.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-CanvasTaskGrid] Screen reader announcement when all rows are collapsed","MyTasksEmptyState_ImportantTitle":"No tasks are marked as important","_MyTasksEmptyState_ImportantTitle.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-MyTasksEmptyState] Title shown in the new MyTasks list view when the Important pivot has no tasks","MyTasksEmptyState_ImportantDescription":"Tasks you mark as important will show up here.","_MyTasksEmptyState_ImportantDescription.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-MyTasksEmptyState] Description shown in the new MyTasks list view when the Important pivot has no tasks","MyTasksEmptyState_DueSoonTitle":"No tasks due soon","_MyTasksEmptyState_DueSoonTitle.comment":"{\\"Ambiguity\\":{\\"due\\":\\"scheduled for a certain date\\"}}{\\"Ambiguity\\":{\\"soon\\":\\"in a short time\\"}}[TAG:APPS-Planner-MyTasksEmptyState] Title shown in the new MyTasks list view when the Due soon pivot has no tasks","MyTasksEmptyState_DueSoonDescription":"Tasks due within the next week will show up here.","_MyTasksEmptyState_DueSoonDescription.comment":"{\\"Ambiguity\\":{\\"due\\":\\"scheduled for a certain date\\"}}[TAG:APPS-Planner-MyTasksEmptyState] Description shown in the new MyTasks list view when the Due soon pivot has no tasks","MyTasksEmptyState_AssignedToMeTitle":"No assigned tasks yet","_MyTasksEmptyState_AssignedToMeTitle.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-MyTasksEmptyState] Title shown in the new MyTasks list view when the Assigned to me pivot has no tasks","MyTasksEmptyState_AssignedToMeDescription":"Team members can assign tasks to you, and you can assign tasks to yourself.","_MyTasksEmptyState_AssignedToMeDescription.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-MyTasksEmptyState] Description shown in the new MyTasks list view when the Assigned to me pivot has no tasks","MyTasksEmptyState_AllTitle":"No tasks yet","_MyTasksEmptyState_AllTitle.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-MyTasksEmptyState] Title shown in the new MyTasks list view when the All pivot has no tasks","MyTasksEmptyState_AllDescription":"Add tasks to start tracking your work and goals.","_MyTasksEmptyState_AllDescription.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-MyTasksEmptyState] Description shown in the new MyTasks list view when the All pivot has no tasks","MyTasksEmptyState_PrivateTasksTitle":"No private tasks yet","_MyTasksEmptyState_PrivateTasksTitle.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-MyTasksEmptyState] Title shown in the new MyTasks list view when the Private tasks pivot has no tasks","MyTasksEmptyState_PrivateTasksDescription":"Tasks you create privately will show up here.","_MyTasksEmptyState_PrivateTasksDescription.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-MyTasksEmptyState] Description shown in the new MyTasks list view when the Private tasks pivot has no tasks","MyTasksEmptyState_FlaggedEmailsTitle":"No flagged emails","_MyTasksEmptyState_FlaggedEmailsTitle.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-MyTasksEmptyState] Title shown in the new MyTasks list view when the Flagged emails pivot has no flagged emails","MyTasksEmptyState_FlaggedEmailsDescription":"Emails you flag in Outlook will show up here as tasks.","_MyTasksEmptyState_FlaggedEmailsDescription.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-MyTasksEmptyState] Description shown in the new MyTasks list view when the Flagged emails pivot has no flagged emails","TaskRecurrence_TaskRecurrenceLabel":"Repeat","_TaskRecurrence_TaskRecurrenceLabel.comment":"The label for the recurrence dropdown","TaskRecurrence_TaskRecurrenceState_DoesNotRepeat":"Does not repeat","_TaskRecurrence_TaskRecurrenceState_DoesNotRepeat.comment":"One of the options in the task recurrence state drop down. Represents \\"Does not repeat\\" state","TaskRecurrence_TaskRecurrenceState_Daily":"Daily","_TaskRecurrence_TaskRecurrenceState_Daily.comment":"One of the options in the task recurrence state drop down. Represents \\"Daily\\" state","TaskRecurrence_TaskRecurrenceState_Weekdays":"Weekdays","_TaskRecurrence_TaskRecurrenceState_Weekdays.comment":"One of the options in the task recurrence state drop down. Represents \\"Weekdays\\" state","TaskRecurrence_TaskRecurrenceState_Weekly":"Weekly","_TaskRecurrence_TaskRecurrenceState_Weekly.comment":"One of the options in the task recurrence state drop down. Represents \\"Weekly\\" state","TaskRecurrence_TaskRecurrenceState_Monthly":"Monthly","_TaskRecurrence_TaskRecurrenceState_Monthly.comment":"One of the options in the task recurrence state drop down. Represents \\"Monthly\\" state","TaskRecurrence_TaskRecurrenceState_Yearly":"Yearly","_TaskRecurrence_TaskRecurrenceState_Yearly.comment":"One of the options in the task recurrence state drop down. Represents \\"Yearly\\" state","TaskRecurrence_TaskRecurrenceState_Custom":"Custom","_TaskRecurrence_TaskRecurrenceState_Custom.comment":"One of the options in the task recurrence state drop down. Represents \\"Custom\\" state","TaskRecurrence_DeleteTaskTitle":"Delete repeating task","_TaskRecurrence_DeleteTaskTitle.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Todoweb-DeleteTask] Title for the delete task dialog.","TaskRecurrence_ClearRecurrenceFromDueDateRemovalTitle":"This removes all future tasks","_TaskRecurrence_ClearRecurrenceFromDueDateRemovalTitle.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Todoweb-DeleteTask] Title for the remove recurrence dialog.","TaskRecurrence_ClearRecurrenceFromDueDateRemovalBody":"Removing the due date of this task removes all future tasks in this series.","_TaskRecurrence_ClearRecurrenceFromDueDateRemovalBody.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Todoweb-DeleteTask] Body text for the remove recurrence dialog.","TaskRecurrence_ClearRecurrenceFromDueDateRemovalButton":"Remove","_TaskRecurrence_ClearRecurrenceFromDueDateRemovalButton.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Todoweb-DeleteTask] Remove button text in remove recurrence dialog.","TaskRecurrence_DeleteTaskOptionForTask":"This task","_TaskRecurrence_DeleteTaskOptionForTask.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Todoweb-DeleteTask] Option for the delete task itself.","TaskRecurrence_DeleteTaskOptionForSeries":"This and all future tasks in series","_TaskRecurrence_DeleteTaskOptionForSeries.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Todoweb-DeleteTask] Option for the delete task series.","TaskRecurrence_DeleteTaskConfirm":"Delete","_TaskRecurrence_DeleteTaskConfirm.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Todoweb-DeleteTask] Confirm button text in delete task dialog.","TaskRecurrence_DeleteTaskCancel":"Cancel","_TaskRecurrence_DeleteTaskCancel.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Todoweb-DeleteTask] Cancel button text in for delete task dialog.","TaskRecurrence_CustomRecurrenceDialogTitle":"Custom repeat","_TaskRecurrence_CustomRecurrenceDialogTitle.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Todoweb-CustomRecurrence] Title for the custom recurrence dialog.","TaskRecurrence_RepeatLabel":"Repeats every","_TaskRecurrence_RepeatLabel.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Todoweb-CustomRecurrence] Label for the section to set the repeat values of the task recurrence.","TaskRecurrence_WeekdayPickerLabel":"On","_TaskRecurrence_WeekdayPickerLabel.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Todoweb-CustomRecurrence] Label for the section to set the weekday values of the task recurrence. This text is followed by a week day picker element.","TaskRecurrence_DayRepeatOptionText":"Day","_TaskRecurrence_DayRepeatOptionText.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Todoweb-CustomRecurrence] Text for the daily repeat dropdown option.","TaskRecurrence_WeekRepeatOptionText":"Week","_TaskRecurrence_WeekRepeatOptionText.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Todoweb-CustomRecurrence] Text for the weekly repeat dropdown option.","TaskRecurrence_MonthRepeatOptionText":"Month","_TaskRecurrence_MonthRepeatOptionText.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Todoweb-CustomRecurrence] Text for the monthly repeat dropdown option.","TaskRecurrence_YearRepeatOptionText":"Year","_TaskRecurrence_YearRepeatOptionText.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Todoweb-CustomRecurrence] Text for the yearly repeat dropdown option.","TaskRecurrence_RecurrenceSummaryText":"Occurs every {0}.","_TaskRecurrence_RecurrenceSummaryText.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Todoweb-CustomRecurrence] Text that summarizes the repeat set for this task. {0} is replaced with the pattern of the repeat (Daily|Weekly|Monthly|Yearly).","TaskRecurrence_DailyPatternTextSingular":"day","_TaskRecurrence_DailyPatternTextSingular.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Todoweb-CustomRecurrence] Text that describes the daily repeat pattern for 1 day repeat interval.","TaskRecurrence_DailyPatternTextPlural":"{0} days","_TaskRecurrence_DailyPatternTextPlural.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Todoweb-CustomRecurrence] Text that describes the daily repeat pattern for repeat intervals over 1 day. {0} is replaced with the number of days.","TaskRecurrence_WeeklyPatternTextSingular":"week on {0}","_TaskRecurrence_WeeklyPatternTextSingular.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Todoweb-CustomRecurrence] Text that describes the singular repeat interval for the weekly pattern. {0} is replaced with the one or many days of the week (ex: \\"Monday\\" or \\"Sunday and Saturday\\" or \\"Monday, Tuesday, Wednesday\\").","TaskRecurrence_WeeklyPatternTextPlural":"{0} weeks on {1}","_TaskRecurrence_WeeklyPatternTextPlural.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Todoweb-CustomRecurrence] Text that describes the plural repeat interval for the weekly pattern. {0} is the number of weeks. {1} is replaced with a single day of the week (ex: \\"Monday\\").","TaskRecurrence_WeekdaySpecifierForTwoValues":"{0} and {1}","_TaskRecurrence_WeekdaySpecifierForTwoValues.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Todoweb-CustomRecurrence] Text that describes the weekdays for the weekly pattern, when 2 weekdays are specified. {0} and {1} are both replaced with different weekday names (ex: \\"Monday\\"). Used in WeeklyPatternTextSingular.","TaskRecurrence_WeekdaySpecifierForPluralValues":"{0}and {1}","_TaskRecurrence_WeekdaySpecifierForPluralValues.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Todoweb-CustomRecurrence] Text that describes the weekdays for the weekly pattern, when 2 or more weekdays are specified. {0}  is replaced with one or more weekday names separated by commas (or other list separator), and {1} is replaced with the last weekday name (ex: \\"Monday, Tuesday, and Saturday\\"). Used in WeeklyPatternTextSingular.","TaskRecurrence_WeekdaySpecifierListSeparator":", ","_TaskRecurrence_WeekdaySpecifierListSeparator.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Todoweb-CustomRecurrence] Used for text that describes the weekdays for the weekly pattern, when 3 or more weekdays are specified. This value is placed between weekday names. Used in WeeklyPatternTextSingular.","TaskRecurrence_AbsoluteMonthlyPatternTextSingular":"month on day {0}","_TaskRecurrence_AbsoluteMonthlyPatternTextSingular.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Todoweb-CustomRecurrence] Text that describes the singular repeat interval for the monthly pattern. {0} is replaced with the day of the month (ex: \\"15\\").","TaskRecurrence_AbsoluteMonthlyPatternTextPlural":"{0} months on day {1}","_TaskRecurrence_AbsoluteMonthlyPatternTextPlural.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Todoweb-CustomRecurrence] Text that describes the plural repeat interval for the monthly pattern, for intervals over 1. {0} is the number of months in the interval. {1} is replaced with the day of the month (ex: \\"15\\").","TaskRecurrence_RelativeMonthlyPatternTextSingular":"month on the {0} {1}","_TaskRecurrence_RelativeMonthlyPatternTextSingular.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Todoweb-CustomRecurrence] Text that describes the singular repeat interval for the monthly pattern. {0} is the ordinal number representing the week index (ex: \\"first\\"). {1} is replaced with a single day of the week (ex: \\"Monday\\").","TaskRecurrence_RelativeMonthlyPatternTextPlural":"{0} months on the {1} {2}","_TaskRecurrence_RelativeMonthlyPatternTextPlural.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Todoweb-CustomRecurrence] Text that describes the plural repeat interval for the monthly pattern, for intervals over 1. {0} is the number of months in the interval. {1} is the ordinal number representing the week index (ex: \\"first\\"). {2} is replaced with a single day of the week (ex: \\"Monday\\").","TaskRecurrence_AbsoluteYearlyPatternTextSingular":"year on {0} {1}","_TaskRecurrence_AbsoluteYearlyPatternTextSingular.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Todoweb-CustomRecurrence] Text that describes the singular repeat interval for the yearly pattern. {0} is replaced with the month (ex: \\"January\\"). {1} is replaced with the day of the month (ex: \\"15\\").","TaskRecurrence_AbsoluteYearlyPatternTextPlural":"{0} years on {1} {2}","_TaskRecurrence_AbsoluteYearlyPatternTextPlural.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Todoweb-CustomRecurrence] Text that describes the repeat interval for the yearly pattern, for intervals over 1. {0} is the number of years in the interval. {1} is replaced with the month (ex: \\"January\\"). {2} is replaced with the day of the month (ex: \\"15\\").","TaskRecurrence_RelativeYearlyPatternTextSingular":"year on the {0} {1} of {2}","_TaskRecurrence_RelativeYearlyPatternTextSingular.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Todoweb-CustomRecurrence] Text that describes the singular repeat interval for the yearly pattern. {0} is the ordinal number representing the week index (ex: \\"first\\"). {1} is replaced with a single day of the week (ex: \\"Monday\\"). {2} is the month (ex: \\"January\\").","TaskRecurrence_RelativeYearlyPatternTextPlural":"{0} years on the {1} {2} of {3}","_TaskRecurrence_RelativeYearlyPatternTextPlural.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Todoweb-CustomRecurrence] Text that describes the repeat interval for the yearly pattern, for intervals over 1. {0} is the number of years in the interval. {1} is the ordinal number representing the week index (ex: \\"first\\"). {2} is replaced with a single day of the week (ex: \\"Monday\\"). {3} is the month (ex: \\"January\\").","TaskRecurrence_IntervalInputAriaLabel":"Repeat interval","_TaskRecurrence_IntervalInputAriaLabel.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Todoweb-CustomRecurrence] Accessibility text for the repeat interval input.","TaskRecurrence_RepeatPatternDropdownAriaLabel":"Repeat pattern","_TaskRecurrence_RepeatPatternDropdownAriaLabel.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Todoweb-CustomRecurrence] Accessibility text for the repeat pattern dropdown.","TaskRecurrence_IncrementIntervalButtonAriaLabel":"Increment interval","_TaskRecurrence_IncrementIntervalButtonAriaLabel.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Todoweb-CustomRecurrence] Accessibility text for the increment repeat interval button.","TaskRecurrence_DecrementIntervalButtonAriaLabel":"Decrement interval","_TaskRecurrence_DecrementIntervalButtonAriaLabel.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Todoweb-CustomRecurrence] Accessibility text for the decrement repeat interval button.","TaskRecurrence_MonthDropdownAriaLabel":"Month","_TaskRecurrence_MonthDropdownAriaLabel.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Todoweb-CustomRecurrence] Accessibility text for the month dropdown.","TaskRecurrence_DayOfWeekDropdownAriaLabel":"Day of week","_TaskRecurrence_DayOfWeekDropdownAriaLabel.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Todoweb-CustomRecurrence] Accessibility text for the day of week dropdown.","TaskRecurrence_WeekIndexDropdownAriaLabel":"Week of month","_TaskRecurrence_WeekIndexDropdownAriaLabel.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Todoweb-CustomRecurrence] Accessibility text for the week of month dropdown.","TaskRecurrence_WeekdayErrorMessage":"Select at least one day of the week to continue.","_TaskRecurrence_WeekdayErrorMessage.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Todoweb-CustomRecurrence] Error message to show when the no days are selected in the week day picker element.","TaskRecurrence_AbsoluteMonthlyPickerRow":"On day {0}","_TaskRecurrence_AbsoluteMonthlyPickerRow.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Todoweb-CustomRecurrence] Label and ordering for the section to set the absolute monthly values of the task recurrence. {0} will be a numeric picker element to set the day of the month of the recurrence (ex: 1).","TaskRecurrence_AbsoluteYearlyPickerRow":"On {0} {1}","_TaskRecurrence_AbsoluteYearlyPickerRow.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Todoweb-CustomRecurrence] Label and ordering for the section to set the absolute yearly values of the task recurrence. {0} will be a dropdown element to set the month of the recurrence (ex: January). {1} will be a numeric picker element to set the day of the month of the recurrence (ex: 1).","TaskRecurrence_RelativeMonthlyPickerRow":"On the {0} {1}","_TaskRecurrence_RelativeMonthlyPickerRow.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Todoweb-CustomRecurrence] Label and ordering for the section to set the relative monthly values of the task recurrence. {0} will be a ordinal number picker element to set the week index (ex: first). {1} will be a weekday dropdown element to set the relative day of the month of the recurrence (ex: Sunday).","TaskRecurrence_RelativeYearlyPickerRow":"On the {0} {1} of {2}","_TaskRecurrence_RelativeYearlyPickerRow.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Todoweb-CustomRecurrence] Label and ordering for the section to set the relative yearly values of the task recurrence. {0} will be a ordinal number picker element to set the week index (ex: first). {1} will be a weekday dropdown to set the relative day of the month of the recurrence (ex: sunday). {2} will be a month dropdown (ex: January).","TaskRecurrence_FirstWeekOrdinalNumberText":"first","_TaskRecurrence_FirstWeekOrdinalNumberText.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Todoweb-CustomRecurrence] Ordinal number text to describe the first week of the month. Used in RelativeDayOfMonthText.","TaskRecurrence_SecondWeekOrdinalNumberText":"second","_TaskRecurrence_SecondWeekOrdinalNumberText.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Todoweb-CustomRecurrence] Ordinal number text to describe the second week of the month. Used in RelativeDayOfMonthText.","TaskRecurrence_ThirdWeekOrdinalNumberText":"third","_TaskRecurrence_ThirdWeekOrdinalNumberText.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Todoweb-CustomRecurrence] Ordinal number text to describe the third week of the month. Used in RelativeDayOfMonthText.","TaskRecurrence_FourthWeekOrdinalNumberText":"fourth","_TaskRecurrence_FourthWeekOrdinalNumberText.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Todoweb-CustomRecurrence] Ordinal number text to describe the fourth week of the month. Used in RelativeDayOfMonthText.","TaskRecurrence_LastWeekOrdinalNumberText":"last","_TaskRecurrence_LastWeekOrdinalNumberText.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Todoweb-CustomRecurrence] Ordinal number text to describe the last week of the month. Used in RelativeDayOfMonthText.","TaskRecurrence_FirstWeekDropdownOptionText":"First","_TaskRecurrence_FirstWeekDropdownOptionText.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Todoweb-CustomRecurrence] Text for the dropdown option to set the relative monthly values of the task recurrence to the first week of the month.","TaskRecurrence_SecondWeekDropdownOptionText":"Second","_TaskRecurrence_SecondWeekDropdownOptionText.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Todoweb-CustomRecurrence] Text for the dropdown option to set the relative monthly values of the task recurrence to the second week of the month.","TaskRecurrence_ThirdWeekDropdownOptionText":"Third","_TaskRecurrence_ThirdWeekDropdownOptionText.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Todoweb-CustomRecurrence] Text for the dropdown option to set the relative monthly values of the task recurrence to the third week of the month.","TaskRecurrence_FourthWeekDropdownOptionText":"Fourth","_TaskRecurrence_FourthWeekDropdownOptionText.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Todoweb-CustomRecurrence] Text for the dropdown option to set the relative monthly values of the task recurrence to the fourth week of the month.","TaskRecurrence_LastWeekDropdownOptionText":"Last","_TaskRecurrence_LastWeekDropdownOptionText.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Todoweb-CustomRecurrence] Text for the dropdown option to set the relative monthly values of the task recurrence to the last week of the month.","TaskRecurrence_DayO