 by the number of attachments on this task.","ChecklistIndicator_ChecklistIndicatorAriaLabel":" {0} of {1} checklist items complete ","_ChecklistIndicator_ChecklistIndicatorAriaLabel.comment":"[TAG:APPS-ProjectWeb-ChecklistIndicator] Aria label text for the checklist indicator icon on the task card. {0} is replaced by the number of completed checklist items. {1} is replaced by the total number of checklist items.","Teams_TeamText":"Team","_Teams_TeamText.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-Teams] Text for a Microsoft Teams Team.","Teams_ChannelText":"Channel","_Teams_ChannelText.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-Teams] Text for a Microsoft Teams Channel.","TrialExpired_TrialExpiredCalloutTitle":"Subscription needed","_TrialExpired_TrialExpiredCalloutTitle.comment":"[TAG:APPS-UnoTrialExpired-UnoTrialExpiredCallout] The title of trial expired callout","TrialExpired_TrialExpiredCalloutText":"To create a premium plan, you\'ll need a premium subscription.","_TrialExpired_TrialExpiredCalloutText.comment":"[TAG:APPS-UnoTrialExpired-UnoTrialExpiredCallout] The text of trial expired callout.","TrialExpired_BuyNowButtonText":"Buy Now","_TrialExpired_BuyNowButtonText.comment":"[TAG:APPS-UnoTrialExpired-UnoTrialExpiredCallout] The text of buy now button.","TrialExpired_RequestSubscriptionButtonText":"Request a subscription","_TrialExpired_RequestSubscriptionButtonText.comment":"[TAG:APPS-UnoTrialExpired-UnoTrialExpiredCallout] The text of request subscription button.","TrialReminder_ActiveTrialReminderTitle":"Your trial ends soon","_TrialReminder_ActiveTrialReminderTitle.comment":"[TAG:APPS-UnoTrialReminder-UnoTrialReminderCallout] Callout title for active trial.","TrialReminder_ExpiredTrialReminderTitle":"Your trial expired","_TrialReminder_ExpiredTrialReminderTitle.comment":"[TAG:APPS-UnoTrialReminder-UnoTrialReminderCallout] Callout title for expired trial.","TrialReminder_ActiveTrialReminderContent":"You have {0} days left in your trial. To keep access to all features, ask your admin to 