":"[TAG:APPS-UNO-DetailsListColumns] Label text for \\"Status\\" column header.","DetailsListOptions_OpenPlan":"Open","_DetailsListOptions_OpenPlan.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-DetailsListOptions]{\\"Ambiguity\\":{\\"open\\":\\"to begin or initiate something\\"}} Text shown on contextual menu item for a plan. \\"Open\\" is the action to open a plan.","DetailsListOptions_RenamePlan":"Rename","_DetailsListOptions_RenamePlan.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-DetailsListOptions]{\\"Ambiguity\\":{\\"rename\\":\\"to assign a new name to something\\"}} Text shown on contextual menu item for a plan. \\"Rename\\" is the action to edit a plan\'s title.","DetailsListOptions_PinPlan":"Pin plan","_DetailsListOptions_PinPlan.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-DetailsListOptions]{\\"Ambiguity\\":{\\"pin\\":\\"a small pointed object used for fastening or sewing\\"}}{\\"Ambiguity\\":{\\"plan\\":\\"Microsoft Planner plan\\"}} Text shown on contextual menu item for a plan. \\"Pin plan\\" is the action to pin or favorite a plan.","DetailsListOptions_UnpinPlan":"Unpin plan","_DetailsListOptions_UnpinPlan.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-DetailsListOptions]{\\"Ambiguity\\":{\\"Unpin\\":\\"to detach something that is pinned\\"}}{\\"Ambiguity\\":{\\"Plan\\":\\"Microsoft Planner plan\\"}} Text shown on contextual menu item for a plan. \\"Unpin plan\\" is the action to unpin or unfavorite a plan.","DetailsListOptions_CopyLinkToPlan":"Copy link to plan","_DetailsListOptions_CopyLinkToPlan.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-DetailsListOptions]{\\"Ambiguity\\":{\\"copy\\":\\"to duplicate or reproduce\\"}} {\\"Ambiguity\\":{\\"link\\":\\"a hyperlink or URL\\"}}{\\"Ambiguity\\":{\\"plan\\":\\"Microsoft Planner plan\\"}} Text shown on contextual menu item for a plan. \\"Copy link to plan\\" is the action to copy a link to a plan.","DetailsListFooter_ShowMorePlans":"Show more","_DetailsListFooter_ShowMorePlans.comment":"[TAG:APPS-DetailsListFooter] Button text shown on the plans list footer in Recent, Private, or Shared pivots. \\"Show more\\" is the action to request non-MRU user-accessible shared plans to view on the plans list to display additional items. {\\"Ambiguity\\":{\\"show\\":\\"to display or present something\\"}} {\\"Ambiguity\\":{\\"more\\":\\"additional items or details\\"}}","PortfolioItemStatus_NotStarted":"Not Started","_PortfolioItemStatus_NotStarted.comment":"[TAG:APPS-UNO-PortfolioItemStatus] Text for \\"Not Started\\" status of a portfolio item","PortfolioItemStatus_OnTrack":"On Track","_PortfolioItemStatus_OnTrack.comment":"[TAG:APPS-UNO-PortfolioItemStatus] Text for \\"On Track\\" status of a portfolio item","PortfolioItemStatus_AtRisk":"At Risk","_PortfolioItemStatus_AtRisk.comment":"[TAG:APPS-UNO-PortfolioItemStatus] Text for \\"At Risk\\" status of a portfolio item","PortfolioItemStatus_OffTrack":"Off Track","_PortfolioItemStatus_OffTrack.comment":"[TAG:APPS-UNO-PortfolioItemStatus] Text for \\"Off Track\\" status of a portfolio item","PortfolioItemStatus_Closed":"Closed","_PortfolioItemStatus_Closed.comment":"[TAG:APPS-UNO-PortfolioItemStatus] Text for \\"Closed\\" status of a portfolio item","Common_Name":"Name","_Common_Name.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Uno-Common] Label text for a Name field.","Common_MoreOptions":"More options","_Common_MoreOptions.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Uno-Common] Accessibility text for \\"More options\\" button that opens a context menu with additional option buttons.","Common_ValidatorRequiredMessage":"This field is required.","_Common_ValidatorRequiredMessage.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Uno-Common] Error message shown when a required field is empty.","LastAccessed_LastAccessedJustNow":"Just now","_LastAccessed_LastAccessedJustNow.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Uno-LastAccessed] Shown as value for \\"last accessed\\" column cell when current user last accessed their plan no later than 45 seconds ago.","LastAccessed_LastAccessedMinutesAgo":"{0}m ago","_LastAccessed_LastAccessedMinutesAgo.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Uno-LastAccessed] Approximate minutes (m) elapsed in sinc