actly one member. {0} is the member name and {1} is the name of the group.","SharePlanDialog_PlanSharedSuccessMessageDual":"{0} and {1} from the \\"{2}\\" group were added to the plan.","_SharePlanDialog_PlanSharedSuccessMessageDual.comment":"Success message for when a plan is successfully shared with an existing group with exactly two members. {0} is the first member name, {1} is the second member name, and {2} is the name of the group.","SharePlanDialog_PlanSharedSuccessMessagePluralSingularOther":"{0}, {1}, and 1 other from the \\"{2}\\" group were added to the plan.","_SharePlanDialog_PlanSharedSuccessMessagePluralSingularOther.comment":"Success message for when a plan is successfully shared with an existing group with exactly three members. {0} is the first member name, {1} is the second member name, and {2} is the name of the group.","SharePlanDialog_PlanSharedSuccessMessagePlural":"{0}, {1}, and {2} others from the \\"{3}\\" group were added to the plan.","_SharePlanDialog_PlanSharedSuccessMessagePlural.comment":"Success message for when a plan is successfully shared with an existing group with more than three members. {0} is the first member name, {1} is the second member name, {2} is the count of additional members, and {3} is the name of the group.","SharePlanDialog_ErrorPrimaryMessage":"Something went wrong","_SharePlanDialog_ErrorPrimaryMessage.comment":"Primary error message shown on share plan dialog when an error occurs","SharePlanDialog_ErrorSecondaryMessage":"Couldn\'t share your plan. Please try again.","_SharePlanDialog_ErrorSecondaryMessage.comment":"Secondary error message shown on share plan dialog when an error occurs","SharePlanDialog_GoBackButtonText":"Go back","_SharePlanDialog_GoBackButtonText.comment":"Text for the button that takes the user back to the share plan dialog from the error state","SharePlanDialog_TryAgainButtonText":"Try again","_SharePlanDialog_TryAgainButtonText.comment":"Text for the button that retries sharing the plan after an error occurs","SharePlanDialog_ClassificationGuidelines":"Guidelines","_SharePlanDialog_ClassificationGuidelines.comment":"Link to the classification guidelines","SharePlanDialog_ClassificationPlaceholder":"Select a Classification","_SharePlanDialog_ClassificationPlaceholder.comment":"Placeholder for classification dropdown.","SharePlanDialog_SensitivityPlaceholder":"Select a Sensitivity","_SharePlanDialog_SensitivityPlaceholder.comment":"Placeholder for sensitivity dropdown.","SharePlanDialog_SensitivityLabel":"Sensitivity","_SharePlanDialog_SensitivityLabel.comment":"Title of the sensitivity dropdown.","SharePlanDialog_SensitivityGuidelines":"Learn more","_SharePlanDialog_SensitivityGuidelines.comment":"Link to the sensitivity guidelines","SharePlanDialog_Private":"Private","_SharePlanDialog_Private.comment":"Text indicates the group will display private when displaying the privacy level","SharePlanDialog_Public":"Public","_SharePlanDialog_Public.comment":"Text indicates the group will display public when displaying the privacy level","SharePlanDialog_PrivateSecondaryText":"Only members have access","_SharePlanDialog_PrivateSecondaryText.comment":"Secondary text to indicate that only members have access when privacy level is private","SharePlanDialog_PublicSecondaryText":"People in your organization have access","_SharePlanDialog_PublicSecondaryText.comment":"Secondary text to indicate that people in your organization have access when privacy level is public","SharePlanDialog_CloseDialog":"Close dialog","_SharePlanDialog_CloseDialog.comment":"Text for the close button on the dialog header","SharePlanDialog_AccessPrivacyStatement":"Members of this plan are part of the {0} group. Everyone in this group has access to the entire plan and any files, chats, and other materials related to it.","_SharePlanDialog_AccessPrivacyStatement.comment":"Text for the privacy statement for sharing the plan, {0} is the placeholder of the group name","SharePlanDialog_PlannerAccessPrivacyStatement":"Adding members to the plan also adds them to the \\"{0}\\" group. They’ll get access to the entire plan, files, emails, chats, and other shared resources.","_SharePlanDialog_PlannerAccessPrivacyStatement.comment":"Text for the privacy statement for sharing the plan, {0} is the placeholder of the group name","SharePlanDialog_AddPeopleOrAgentText":"Add people or agent","_SharePlanDialog_AddPeopleOrAgentText.comment":"Text proprty to display header to add people and agents","SharePlanDialog_SwitchingGroup_PeopleText":"People","_SharePlanDialog_SwitchingGroup_PeopleText.comment":"Text to display on button to switch group to people.","SharePlanDialog_SwitchingGroup_AgentsText":"Agents","_SharePlanDialog_SwitchingGroup_AgentsText.comment":"Text to display on button to switch group to agents.","SharePlanDialog_AgentsComponent_AddAgentText":"Add agent","_SharePlanDialog_AgentsComponent_AddAgentText.comment":"Text to display on button to add agent.","SharePlanDialog_AgentsComponent_DeleteAgentDialogText":"Remove {0} Agent from the plan?","_SharePlanDialog_AgentsComponent_DeleteAgentDialogText.comment":"Text to display on Delete Dialog. {0} will be replaced with the Agent name to be deleted.","SharePlanDialog_AgentsComponent_DeleteAgentDialogDescriptionText":"This will remove {0} Agent for everyone in this plan.","_SharePlanDialog_AgentsComponent_DeleteAgentDialogDescriptionText.comment":"Text to display on Delete Dialog description. {0} will be replaced with the Agent name to be deleted.","SharePlanDialog_AgentsComponent_PMAAccessPrivacyStatement":"The Planner Agent will automatically collaborate with the agents you add to complete tasks.","_SharePlanDialog_AgentsComponent_PMAAccessPrivacyStatement.comment":"Text for the privacy statement for sharing the plan with Planner Agent.","SharePlanDialog_AgentsComponent_ExtensibleAgentsAccessPrivacyStatement":"Agents added to this plan will have access to the entire plan.","_SharePlanDialog_AgentsComponent_ExtensibleAgentsAccessPrivacyStatement.comment":"Text for the privacy statement for sharing the plan with extensible agents.","SharePlanDialog_AgentsComponent_Heading1":"Do more with Planner Agent by adding agents","_SharePlanDialog_AgentsComponent_Heading1.comment":"Text for the heading of the agents component","SharePlanDialog_AgentsComponent_Heading2":"Agents working with Planner Agent ({0})","_SharePlanDialog_AgentsComponent_Heading2.comment":"Text for the heading of the agents component. {0} will be replaced with the number of agents in the plan.","SharePlanDialog_AgentsComponent_InstalledAgentHeading":"Your installed agents","_SharePlanDialog_AgentsComponent_InstalledAgentHeading.comment":"Text for the heading of the installed agents component","SharePlanDialog_AgentsComponent_NoInstalledAgentText":"No available agents","_SharePlanDialog_AgentsComponent_NoInstalledAgentText.comment":"Text for the no installed agents component","SharePlanDialog_AgentsComponent_MoreAgentsText":"To add more agents, explore","_SharePlanDialog_AgentsComponent_MoreAgentsText.comment":"{\\"Ambiguity\\":{\\"agents\\":\\"software programs or bots that perform automated tasks\\"}}{\\"Ambiguity\\":{\\"explore\\":\\"to investigate or examine thoroughly\\"}} Text for the more agents component.","SharePlanDialog_AgentsComponent_MaxAgentsErrorMessage":"You\'ve reached the maximum number of agents for your plan. To add a new one, please remove an existing agent.","_SharePlanDialog_AgentsComponent_MaxAgentsErrorMessage.comment":"Error message shown when the user tries to add more than the maximum number of agents to a plan.","SharePlanDialog_AgentsComponent_MaxAgentsErrorTitle":"You can\'t add more agents","_SharePlanDialog_AgentsComponent_MaxAgentsErrorTitle.comment":"Error title shown when the user tries to add more than the maximum number of agents to a plan.","SharePlanDialog_AgentsComponent_ErrorCalloutGotItButtonText":"Got it","_SharePlanDialog_AgentsComponent_ErrorCalloutGotItButtonText.comment":"Text for the button to close the error callout","SharePlanDialog_OpenGroupTooltip":"View shared emails, files, and other group details.","_SharePlanDialog_OpenGroupTooltip.comment":"Tooltip text for the button to open the Microsoft 365 group associated with the plan.","SharePlanDialog_PluralMembersCount":"{0} members","_SharePlanDialog_PluralMembersCount.comment":"Text to display the number of members in a group. {0} will be replaced with the number of members.","SharePlanDialog_SingularMembersCount":"1 member","_SharePlanDialog_SingularMembersCount.comment":"Text to display when there is one member in a group.","SharePlanDialog_ErrorHeaderText":"Your plan wasn\'t shared","_SharePlanDialog_ErrorHeaderText.comment":"Header text on the share plan dialog when a plan fails to be shared","SharePlanDialog_CreateGroupDisabledTooltip":"Your organization doesn\'t allow creating a new group.","_SharePlanDialog_CreateGroupDisabledTooltip.comment":"Tooltip text indicating that the user cannot create a new group because their organization has disabled this feature.","TeamsStore":"Apps in Teams","_TeamsStore.comment":"{\\"Ambiguity\\":{\\"Apps\\":\\"software applications\\"}}{\\"Ambiguity\\":{\\"Teams\\":\\"Microsoft Teams (collaboration platform)\\"}}Text for apps in Teams Store.","UnknownText":"Unknown","_UnknownText.comment":"Text for unknown","AddText":"Add","_AddText.comment":"Add string used in the context of adding something, such as an agent, group etc.","FREDialog_ContentTitle":"Welcome to Planner!","_FREDialog_ContentTitle.comment":"{PlaceHolder=!fr,ru;\\"Planner\\"}[BRANDING][TAG:APPS-Planner-FREDialog] Title for the FRE dialog","FREDialog_ContentText":"Manage all your work in one place with Planner","_FREDialog_ContentText.comment":"{PlaceHolder=\\"Planner\\"}[BRANDING][TAG:APPS-Planner-FREDialog] Text for the FRE dialog","FREDialog_ContentTextInfo":"{0} {1}","_FREDialog_ContentTextInfo.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-FREDialog] A standard string of in the format of \\"ContentMain: ContentLine\\". {0} will be replaced by ContentTextMain. {1} will be replaced by ContentTextLine","FREDialog_ContentTextLine1":"Set goals and track progress across Microsoft 365 apps like Teams, Outlook, Loop, and more.","_FREDialog_ContentTextLine1.comment":"{PlaceHolder=\\"Teams, Outlook, Loop\\"}[BRANDING][TAG:APPS-Planner-FREDialog] Text for the first line in the FRE dialog main content","FREDialog_ContentTextLine2":"Let AI-powered planning handle the busywork, so you and your team can focus.","_FREDialog_ContentTextLine2.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-FREDialog] Text for the first line in the FRE dialog main content","FREDialog_ContentTextLink":"Learn more about the new Planner","_FREDialog_ContentTextLink.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-FREDialog] Text for the link in the FRE dialog","FREDialog_PrimaryButtonText":"Get started","_FREDialog_PrimaryButtonText.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-FREDialog] Text for the primary button in the FRE dialog","TaskAssignmentControl_AssignTooManyErrorMessage":"You can\'t assign more than {0} people to a single task.","_TaskAssignmentControl_AssignTooManyErrorMessage.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-AssignControl] Content in an error dialog that pops up when a user has tried to assign a task to too many people. {0} will be replaced with the maximum number of assignees","TaskAssignmentControl_AssignErrorHeader":"Oops","_TaskAssignmentControl_AssignErrorHeader.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-AssignControl] Header for error dialog, expresses that an error occurred","TaskAssignmentControl_NoPlanSelectedError":"Select a plan","_TaskAssignmentControl_NoPlanSelectedError.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-PlanGridCell] The text of the validator callout informs that the plan was not selected.","TaskAssignmentFacepile_AssignedTo":"Assigned to {0}","TaskAssignmentFacepile_AssignedTo.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-AssignControl] Text pattern for displaying assigned users in a facepile. {0} will be replaced with the assigned users.","SharedContainersList_SharedWithHeader":"Shared with","_SharedContainersList_SharedWithHeader.comment":"Text for the header of the shared container list","SharedWithFileContainers_Header":"Meeting notes:","_SharedWithFileContainers_Header.comment":"Text for the header of the shared with file containers list","SharedWithFileContainers_PlanSharedWithFilesMessage":"This plan includes tasks from a \\"{0}\\" meeting instance. People with access to its meeting notes are added to this plan.","_SharedWithFileContainers_PlanSharedWithFilesMessage.comment":"Message indicating that the plan is shared with files, and that users with access to the files can also access the plan. {0} will be replaced with the meeting name.","SharedWithFileContainers_LearnMore":"Learn about shared task lists.","_SharedWithFileContainers_LearnMore.comment":"Link text for learn more about shared task lists.","SharedContainersList_PlanSharedWithFilesMessage":"This plan has been shared with one or more files. People with access to these files can also view and edit this plan.","_SharedContainersList_PlanSharedWithFilesMessage.comment":"Message indicating that the plan is shared with files, and that users with access to the files can also access the plan.","OverflowCount":"+{0}","_OverflowCount.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-Common] Text pattern for displaying overflow count. {0} will be replaced with the number of additional items.","SharedContainersList_UnsharedFileMessageSingular":"other file you do not have access to.","_SharedContainersList_UnsharedFileMessageSingular.comment":"Message indicating the user does not have access to a file shared with the plan. This string is displayed beside \\"PlusNumberOfUnsharedFiles\\", e.g. \\"+1 other file you do not have access to\\".","SharedContainersList_UnsharedFileMessagePlural":"other files you do not have access to.","_SharedContainersList_UnsharedFileMessagePlural.comment":"Message indicating the user does not have access to files shared with the plan. This string is displayed beside \\"PlusNumberOfUnsharedFiles\\", e.g. \\"+2 other files you do not have access to\\".","SharedContainersList_UnsharedFileFullMessageSingular":"This plan has been shared with 1 file you do not have access to. People with access to this file can view and edit this plan.","_SharedContainersList_UnsharedFileFullMessageSingular.comment":"Message indicating the user does not have access to a single file shared with the plan.","SharedContainersList_UnsharedFileFullMessagePlural":"This plan has been shared with {0} files you do not have access to. People with access to these files can view and edit this plan.","_SharedContainersList_UnsharedFileFullMessagePlural.comment":"Message indicating the user does not have access to multiple files shared with the plan. {0} will be replaced with the number of files.","SharedContainersList_LearnMore":"Learn more","_SharedContainersList_LearnMore.comment":"Text for learn more link displayed after a message.","SharedContainersList_LearnMoreAboutRecurrence":"Learn about repeat tasks.","_SharedContainersList_LearnMoreAboutRecurrence.comment":"Text for learn more about repeat link displayed after a message.","AssignTaskConfirmationDialog_AssignTaskConfirmationTitle":"Assign task to the user?","_AssignTaskConfirmationDialog_AssignTaskConfirmationTitle.comment":"Title for the assign task confirmation dialog.","AssignTaskConfirmationDialog_AssignTaskConfirmationMessage":"If this user doesn\'t have access to this plan, they can see this task in My Tasks","_AssignTaskConfirmationDialog_AssignTaskConfirmationMessage.comment":"Message for the assign task confirmation dialog.","AssignTaskConfirmationDialog_AssignTaskConfirmationOK":"Assign","_AssignTaskConfirmationDialog_AssignTaskConfirmationOK.comment":"OK button - continue the action of assigning the task.","AssignTaskConfirmationDialog_AssignTaskConfirmationCancel":"Cancel","_AssignTaskConfirmationDialog_AssignTaskConfirmationCancel.comment":"Cancel button - cancel the action of assigning the task.","ShareFileWarningDialog_ShareFileAndAssignTaskWarningTitle":"Assign task and share file?","_ShareFileWarningDialog_ShareFileAndAssignTaskWarningTitle.comment":"Title for the share file and assign task warning dialog. Assigner is not a plan roster member (has access via a shared file) and cannot confirm if the assignee has plan access.","ShareFileWarningDialog_ShareFileAndAssignTaskWarningMessage":"We couldn\'t confirm that this user has access to this plan. Assigning this task will give them edit access to the file linked above and grants them edit access to this plan while they have access to the file.","_ShareFileWarningDialog_ShareFileAndAssignTaskWarningMessage.comment":"Message shown in the body of the share file and assign task warning dialog. Assigner is not a plan roster member (has access via a shared file) and cannot confirm if the assignee has plan access.","ShareFileWarningDialog_ShareFileAndAssignTaskOK":"Assign and share","_ShareFileWarningDialog_ShareFileAndAssignTaskOK.comment":"OK button - continue the action of sharing the file with the assignee.","ShareFileWarningDialog_ShareFileAndAssignTaskCancel":"Cancel","_ShareFileWarningDialog_ShareFileAndAssignTaskCancel.comment":"Cancel button - cancel the action of sharing the file with the assignee.","AddNonMemberWarningDialog_AddNonMemberWarningTitle":"Assign task and add user to plan?","_AddNonMemberWarningDialog_AddNonMemberWarningTitle.comment":"Title for the add non-member warning dialog. user refers to anyone who\'s not a member or owner of this group / plan. This includes guests of this group, and anyone outside of the group.","AddNonMemberWarningDialog_HostContainerAccessOnlyMessage":"This user isn\'t a member of this plan. Assigning this task will add the user to this plan and its associated group membership. This will give the user access to all plan data, including any files and Teams channels.","_AddNonMemberWarningDialog_HostContainerAccessOnlyMessage.comment":"Message shown in the body add non-member warning dialog, when the assigner has plan access via the host container only. User refers to anyone who\'s not a member or owner of this group / plan. This includes guests of this group, and anyone outside of the group.","AddNonMemberWarningDialog_HostAndSharedContainerAccessMessage":"This user isn\'t a member of this plan. Assigning the task will add the user to the plan and give them access to all plan data. Or you can also share a file from this plan to give them access before trying again.","_AddNonMemberWarningDialog_HostAndSharedContainerAccessMessage.comment":"Message shown in the body add non-member warning dialog, when the assigner has plan access via both the host container and a shared container. User refers to anyone who\'s not a member or owner of this group / plan. This includes guests of this group, and anyone outside of the group.","AddNonMemberWarningDialog_AddNonMemberOK":"Assign and add","_AddNonMemberWarningDialog_AddNonMemberOK.comment":"OK button - continue the action.","AddNonMemberWarningDialog_AddNonMemberCancel":"Cancel","_AddNonMemberWarningDialog_AddNonMemberCancel.comment":"Cancel button - cancel the action.","AddNonMemberWarningDialog_UnsharedPlanTitle":"Plan has not been shared yet","_AddNonMemberWarningDialog_UnsharedPlanTitle.comment":"Title for the add non-member warning dialog when the plan has not been shared yet.","AddNonMemberWarningDialog_UnsharedPlanText":"Before you can assign this task to someone, the plan needs to be shared with a group. You can create a new group or share with an existing group.","_AddNonMemberWarningDialog_UnsharedPlanText.comment":"Message shown in the body add non-member warning dialog when the plan has not been shared yet.","AddNonMemberWarningDialog_CreateGroupOKText":"Add a group","_AddNonMemberWarningDialog_CreateGroupOKText.comment":"Text for the button to create a group when assigning a task to a non-member of the plan.","BasicTaskActionCreator_CreateApproval_AttachmentName":"View task: {0}","_BasicTaskActionCreator_CreateApproval_AttachmentName.comment":"The attachment name string generated when creating an approval for a task","BasicTaskActionCreator_CreateApproval_Details":"The {0} team has completed this work. Please review the work and approve or reject. When you approve, the task will be marked complete","_BasicTaskActionCreator_CreateApproval_Details.comment":"The detail string generated when creating an approval for a task","TaskCard_MovableTaskCardAriaLabel":", Use tab key to access a task card, left and right arrow keys to access important task information, press enter to access all task details, use Ctrl+up arrow and Ctrl+down arrow to move the task up or down.","_TaskCard_MovableTaskCardAriaLabel.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Todoweb-Shared] Accessibility text for the movable task card.","TaskCard_TaskCardAriaLabel":", Use tab key to access a task card, left and right arrow keys to access important task information, press enter to access all task details.","_TaskCard_TaskCardAriaLabel.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Todoweb-Shared] Accessibility text for the task card.","TaskBoardColumn_RenameBucket":"Rename","_TaskBoardColumn_RenameBucket.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Todoweb-Taskboard] Menu item in the dropdown for renaming bucket","TaskBoardColumn_DeleteBucket":"Delete","_TaskBoardColumn_DeleteBucket.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Todoweb-Taskboard] Menu item in the dropdown for deleting a bucket","TaskBoardColumn_MoveBucketRight":"Move right","_TaskBoardColumn_MoveBucketRight.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Todoweb-Taskboard] Menu item in the dropdown for moving a bucket right","TaskBoardColumn_MoveBucketLeft":"Move left","_TaskBoardColumn_MoveBucketLeft.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Todoweb-Taskboard] Menu item in the dropdown for moving a bucket left","TaskBoardColumn_BucketColorPickerAriaLabel":"Set bucket color","_TaskBoardColumn_BucketColorPickerAriaLabel.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Todoweb-Taskboard] Aria label for the button that opens the bucket color picker","TaskBoardColumn_BucketColorPickerNoColor":"No color","_TaskBoardColumn_BucketColorPickerNoColor.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Todoweb-Taskboard] Label for the option to remove color from a bucket column","TaskBoardColumn_EditTitleAriaLabel":"Column title","_TaskBoardColumn_EditTitleAriaLabel.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Todoweb-Taskboard] Accessibility text for the text field where a column\'s title will be renamed","TaskBoardView_EmptyBoardTitle":"Let\'s create your first bucket","_TaskBoardView_EmptyBoardTitle.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-Board] Title shown when the board has no buckets and is grouped by bucket","TaskBoardView_EmptyBoardDescription":"Organize your tasks into buckets to keep your board structured.","_TaskBoardView_EmptyBoardDescription.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-Board] Description shown when the board has no buckets and is grouped by bucket","TaskBoardColumn_AddNewBucket":"Add a new bucket","_TaskBoardColumn_AddNewBucket.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Todoweb-Taskboard] Accessibility - name for the Add new bucket button","TaskBoardColumn_AddNewBucketPlaceHolder":"Bucket name","_TaskBoardColumn_AddNewBucketPlaceHolder.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Todoweb-Taskboard] Place holder text in create bucket box in taskboard","TaskBoardColumn_DeleteBucketText":"Delete {0}?","_TaskBoardColumn_DeleteBucketText.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Todoweb-Taskboard] Text for header of delete bucket dialog. {0} will be replaced with the bucket name","TaskBoardColumn_DeleteBucketTitle":"Delete bucket and all its tasks?","_TaskBoardColumn_DeleteBucketTitle.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Todoweb-Taskboard] Text for title of delete bucket confirmation dialog.","TaskBoardColumn_DeleteBucketTasksSubtext":"This deletes the \\"{0}\\" bucket and all the tasks inside it","_TaskBoardColumn_DeleteBucketTasksSubtext.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Todoweb-Taskboard] Text for the subtext of delete bucket dialog. {0} will be replaced with the bucket name","TaskBoardColumn_DeleteUncategorizedTitle":"Delete uncategorized tasks?","_TaskBoardColumn_DeleteUncategorizedTitle.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Todoweb-Taskboard] Text for title of delete uncategorized tasks confirmation dialog.","TaskBoardColumn_DeleteUncategorizedTasksSubtext":"All tasks in this bucket will be deleted.","_TaskBoardColumn_DeleteUncategorizedTasksSubtext.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Todoweb-Taskboard] Subtext for the delete uncategorized tasks confirmation dialog.","TaskBoardColumn_DeleteBucketTasksText":"All tasks in this bucket will also be deleted.","_TaskBoardColumn_DeleteBucketTasksText.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Todoweb-Taskboard] Text for delete bucket dialog","TaskBoardColumn_DeleteBucketButtonText":"Delete","_TaskBoardColumn_DeleteBucketButtonText.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Todoweb-Taskboard] Text for delete bucket button in taskboard","TaskBoardColumn_CancelDelete":"Cancel","_TaskBoardColumn_CancelDelete.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Todoweb-Taskboard] Text for cancel delete bucket dialog in taskboard","TaskBoardColumn_AddTaskButtonText":"Add task","_TaskBoardColumn_AddTaskButtonText.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-Board] Label for the add task button","TaskBoardColumn_AddButtonContainerAriaLabel":"Add task card in {0} column","_TaskBoardColumn_AddButtonContainerAriaLabel.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-Board] Accessibility - Add task card button description for speech reader. {0} will be replaced with the title of a column (it can be a bucket, user name, or progress)","TaskBoardColumn_DisabledAddButtonTooltipText":"Add task is disabled for this scenario.","_TaskBoardColumn_DisabledAddButtonTooltipText.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-Board] Accessibility - Add task card button description when it is disabled.","TaskBoardColumn_AddTaskDisabledForFlaggedEmail":"Flag an email in Outlook to add it here as a task.","_TaskBoardColumn_AddTaskDisabledForFlaggedEmail.comment":"{PlaceHolder=\\"Outlook\\"}[Branding][TAG:APPS-Planner-Board] Accessibility - Add task card button description when it is disabled.","TaskBoardColumn_AddButtonContainerTooltipText":"Add a task","_TaskBoardColumn_AddButtonContainerTooltipText.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-Board] Accessibility - Add task card button description for tooltip text.","TaskBoardColumn_ColumnTitleAriaLabel":"Column {0}","_TaskBoardColumn_ColumnTitleAriaLabel.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-Board] Accessibility text for the column title. {0} is the name of the selected column.","TaskBoardColumn_ColumnAriaLabel":", Use Ctrl+Shift+Comma and Ctrl+Shift+Period to move this column left or right.","_TaskBoardColumn_ColumnAriaLabel.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-Board] Accessibility text for the column. Comma refers to the comma key on the keyboard. Period refers to the period key on the keyboard.","TaskBoardColumn_EvoColumnAriaLabel":", Use Ctrl+Alt+Comma and Ctrl+Alt+Period to move this column left or right.","_TaskBoardColumn_EvoColumnAriaLabel.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-Board] Accessibility text for the column. Comma refers to the comma key on the keyboard. Period refers to the period key on the keyboard.","TaskBoardColumn_MoreOptionsAriaLabel":"More options","_TaskBoardColumn_MoreOptionsAriaLabel.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Todoweb-Taskboard] Accessibility text for the more options button","TaskBoardColumn_CompletedSectionText":"Completed tasks","_TaskBoardColumn_CompletedSectionText.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Todoweb-Taskboard] Text on the completed tasks section","TaskBoardColumn_ChangeToGroupByPlanTooltipText":"To add new tasks, change the view to group by plan","_TaskBoardColumn_ChangeToGroupByPlanTooltipText.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-Board] Tooltip text for the disabled add task button when grouping by plan is not selected","TaskBoard_AddTaskDisabledPremiumPlanTooltip":"Add tasks by opening the premium plan","_TaskBoard_AddTaskDisabledPremiumPlanTooltip.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-Board] Tooltip text for the disabled add task button when viewing a premium plan from MyTasks view","ToastNotifcations_AddTaskErrorToastTitle":"Your task needs a name","_ToastNotifcations_AddTaskErrorToastTitle.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-SharedComponents] Title for the toast notification for add task error.","ScheduledOccurrenceEditRecipientsConfirmationDialogTitle":"Recipient list updated","_ScheduledOccurrenceEditRecipientsConfirmationDialogTitle.comment":"Title for the updating the recipient list confirmation dialog","ScheduledOccurrenceEditRecipientsConfirmationDialogText_mf":"An occurrence named {publicationName} is already scheduled for this series. Apply these changes to that occurrence too?","_ScheduledOccurrenceEditRecipientsConfirmationDialog_mf.comment":"{publicationName} is the scheduled occurrence","ScheduledOccurrenceEditRecipientsConfirmButton":"Done","_ScheduledOccurrenceEditRecipientsConfirmButton.comment":"Label for the button on the confirmation dialog to be done","ScheduledOccurrenceEditRecipientsYesChoice":"Yes","_ScheduledOccurrenceEditRecipientsYesChoice.comment":"Label for the choice to edit recipients for the scheduled occurrence","ScheduledOccurrenceEditRecipientsNoChoice":"No","_ScheduledOccurrenceEditRecipientsNoChoice.comment":"Label for the choice to not edit recipients for the scheduled occurrence","ErrorUpdatingEditRecipientsOccurrenceDialogTitle":"Something went wrong","_ErrorUpdatingEditRecipientsOccurrenceDialogTitle.comment":"Title for the error dialog, when updating edit recipients for the occurrence fails","ErrorUpdatingEditRecipientsOccurrenceDialogText":"We weren’t able to update the recipients. Would you like to try again?\\nIf you cancel, future occurrences of this list will continue to send the previously selected recipients","_ErrorUpdatingEditRecipientsOccurrenceDialogText.comment":"Text for the error dialog, when updating edit recipients for the occurrence fails","ErrorUpdatingEditRecipientsOccurrenceDialogConfirmButton":"Try again","_ErrorUpdatingEditRecipientsOccurrenceDialogConfirmButton.comment":"Confirm button for the error dialog to try again","ErrorUpdatingEditRecipientsOccurrenceDialogDismissButton":"Cancel","_ErrorUpdatingEditRecipientsOccurrenceDialogDismissButton.comment":"Dismiss button for the error dialog","ConfirmTextScheduledOccurrence_mf":"Save changes for next occurrence of scheduled list:","_ConfirmTextScheduledOccurrence_mf.comment":"Text to display the scheduled occurrence hierarchy is about to update","ConfirmTextPublishingTemplate_mf":"Save changes for recurring list series:","_ConfirmTextPublishingTemplate_mf.comment":"Text to display the publishing template hierarchy is about to update","Save":"Save","_Save.comment":"Text used on a button to save hierarchy publication","Common_Loading":"Loading...","_Common_Loading.comment":"Text used to indicate that the page is loading","Common_PrefixForSmartUrl":"{0} - {1}","_Common_PrefixForSmartUrl.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-Common] Placeholder for prettified task/project link url. {0} is the prefix. {1} is the item name","WhiteboardPage_ErrorText":"Could not load Whiteboard","_WhiteboardPage_ErrorText.comment":"{PlaceHolder=\\"Whiteboard\\"}[BRANDING][TAG:APPS-ProjectWeb-WhiteboardPage] Error message when Whiteboard fails to load","WhiteboardPage_ErrorSubText":"Please try again in some time.","_WhiteboardPage_ErrorSubText.comment":"[TAG:APPS-ProjectWeb-WhiteboardPage] Error subtext message when Whiteboard fails to load","WhiteboardPage_TasksConversion_SuccessMessage":"Notes successfully converted to tasks! You can open Grid view in Planner to see the new tasks","_WhiteboardPage_TasksConversion_SuccessMessage.comment":"Text to inform the user that whiteboard sticky notes are converted into tasks successfully, and to view the converted tasks they can open Grid view in Planner","WhiteboardPage_TasksConversion_FailureMessage":"Failed to convert notes to tasks. Please try again.","_WhiteboardPage_TasksConversion_FailureMessage.comment":"Text to inform user that conversion of sticky notes to tasks failed and requesting them to try again.","WhiteboardPage_TasksConversion_PartialSuccessMessage":"Notes successfully converted to tasks! Some notes had already been converted.","_WhiteboardP