rkflowState_NeedsInput_ColumnName":"Couldn’t complete","_PlannerBoardPage_ProjectManagerWorkflowState_NeedsInput_ColumnName.comment":"Column name for the Planner Agent workflow state Needs your input","PlannerBoardPage_ProjectManagerWorkflowState_Ready_ColumnName":"Ready for review","_PlannerBoardPage_ProjectManagerWorkflowState_Ready_ColumnName.comment":"Column name for the Planner Agent workflow state Ready","Copilot_Copilot":"Copilot","_Copilot_Copilot.comment":"{PlaceHolder=\\"Copilot\\"}[BRANDING][TAG:APPS-Planner-Copilot] Label for the button that opens the Copilot pane and for the Copilot pane\'s header.","Copilot_PreviewTag":"Preview","_Copilot_PreviewTag.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-Copilot] Text that will be placed in a tag next to the Copilot pane\'s header text, indicating that the Copilot feature is in preview mode.","Copilot_ProjectAgent":"Planner Agent","_Copilot_ProjectAgent.comment":"{PlaceHolder=\\"Planner Agent\\"}[BRANDING][TAG:APPS-Planner-Copilot] Label for the button that opens the Planner Agent pane and for the Planner Agent pane\'s header.","Copilot_PrivateTag":"Private","_Copilot_PrivateTag.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-Copilot] Text that will be placed in a tag next to the Planner Agent pane\'s header text, indicating that the Planner Agent feature is private to the user.","TaskDetailsEditorContainer_ClosePaneButtonLabel":"Close pane","_TaskDetailsEditorContainer_ClosePaneButtonLabel.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-TaskDetailsEditorContainer] Label for the button that closes pane","Copilot_PromptLibraryHeader":"Prompts","_Copilot_PromptLibraryHeader.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-Copilot] Header for the prompt library section in the Copilot pane","Copilot_PromptLibraryPrioritizeTitle":"Prioritize","_Copilot_PromptLibraryPrioritizeTitle.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-Copilot] This is a title for a category of Copilot prompts related to task prioritization","Copilot_PromptLibraryPrioritize1":"What should I focus on?","_Copilot_PromptLibraryPrioritize1.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-Copilot] This is a starter prompt specifically aimed at helping users prioritize tasks effectively.","Copilot_PromptLibraryPrioritize2":"What are [the important deadlines in this plan?]","_Copilot_PromptLibraryPrioritize2.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-Copilot] A suggested prompt for a user to ask Copilot. Text within [] will be replaced by the user after selecting this.","Copilot_PromptLibraryUnderstandTitle":"Understand","_Copilot_PromptLibraryUnderstandTitle.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-Copilot] This is a title for a category of Copilot prompts","Copilot_PromptLibraryUnderstand1":"Break down the steps to complete the task [Task Name]","_Copilot_PromptLibraryUnderstand1.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-Copilot]  A starter suggested prompt for a user to ask Copilot. Text within [] will be replaced by the user after selecting this ","Copilot_PromptLibraryUnderstand2":"Give me a status report for this plan [that includes progress, highlights, and risks]","_Copilot_PromptLibraryUnderstand2.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-Copilot] A suggested prompt for a user to ask Copilot. Text within [] will be replaced by the user after selecting this.","Copilot_PromptLibraryAskTitle":"Ask","_Copilot_PromptLibraryAskTitle.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-Copilot] This is a title for a category of Copilot prompts","Copilot_PromptLibraryAsk1":"What are the top techniques for managing my time effectively?","_Copilot_PromptLibraryAsk1.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-Copilot]  A starter suggested prompt for a user to ask Copilot. Text within [] will be replaced by the user after selecting this ","Copilot_PromptLibraryAsk2":"What are some ways to [increase revenue for a restaurant chain?]","_Copilot_PromptLibraryAsk2.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-Copilot] A suggested prompt for a user to ask Copilot. Text within [] will be replaced by the user after selecting this.","Copilot_ZeroPromptSuggestion1":"Review my schedule for today. Suggest when to work on my important tasks.","_Copilot_ZeroPromptSuggestion1.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-Copilot] A suggestion shown to the user before any commands are made to Copilot","Copilot_ZeroPromptSuggestion2":"Which tasks should I work on for my upcoming meetings today?","_Copilot_ZeroPromptSuggestion2.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-Copilot] A suggestion shown to the user before any commands are made to Copilot","Copilot_ZeroPromptSuggestion3":"Which tasks could I work on offline?","_Copilot_ZeroPromptSuggestion3.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-Copilot] A suggestion shown to the user before any commands are made to Copilot","Copilot_ZeroPromptSuggestion4":"Which tasks require collaboration with my team?","_Copilot_ZeroPromptSuggestion4.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-Copilot] A suggestion shown to the user before any commands are made to Copilot","Copilot_ZeroPromptSuggestion5":"Which tasks were assigned to me by my manager?","_Copilot_ZeroPromptSuggestion5.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-Copilot] A suggestion shown to the user before any commands are made to Copilot","Copilot_ZeroPromptSuggestion6":"What are my tasks due today?","_Copilot_ZeroPromptSuggestion6.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-Copilot] A suggestion shown to the user before any commands are made to Copilot","Copilot_ZeroPromptSuggestion7":"Which tasks can I complete quickly?","_Copilot_ZeroPromptSuggestion7.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-Copilot] A suggestion shown to the user before any commands are made to Copilot","Copilot_ZeroPromptSuggestion8":"Which tasks are related to [improving team morale]?","_Copilot_ZeroPromptSuggestion8.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-Copilot] A suggestion shown to the user before any commands are made to Copilot. Text within [] will be replaced by the user after selecting this.","Copilot_ZeroPromptSuggestion9":"Find information that will help me complete the task [Task Name]","_Copilot_ZeroPromptSuggestion9.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-Copilot] A suggestion shown to the user before any commands are made to Copilot. Text within [] will be replaced by the user after selecting this.","Copilot_ZeroPromptSuggestion10":"Explain the requirements of the task [Task Name]","_Copilot_ZeroPromptSuggestion10.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-Copilot] A suggestion shown to the user before any commands are made to Copilot. Text within [] will be replaced by the user after selecting this.","Copilot_ZeroPromptSuggestion11":"What are the potential challenges in completing the task [Task Name]?","_Copilot_ZeroPromptSuggestion11.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-Copilot] A suggestion shown to the user before any commands are made to Copilot. Text within [] will be replaced by the user after selecting this.","Copilot_ZeroPromptSuggestion12":"How can I measure the success of the task [Task Name]?","_Copilot_ZeroPromptSuggestion12.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-Copilot] A suggestion shown to the user before any commands are made to Copilot. Text within [] will be replaced by the user after selecting this.","Copilot_ZeroPromptSuggestion13":"Suggest strategies to stop procrastinating on important tasks","_Copilot_ZeroPromptSuggestion13.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-Copilot] A suggestion shown to the user before any commands are made to Copilot","Copilot_ZeroPromptSuggestion14":"How can I ensure consistent progress on long-term projects","_Copilot_ZeroPromptSuggestion14.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-Copilot] A suggestion shown to the user before any commands are made to Copilot","Copilot_ZeroPromptSuggestion15":"How can I improve my work life balance without affecting productivity","_Copilot_ZeroPromptSuggestion15.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-Copilot] A suggestion shown to the user before any commands are made to Copilot","Copilot_ChatInputPlaceholder":"Start chatting or use / to ask about files or people.","_Copilot_ChatInputPlaceholder.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-Copilot] Placeholder text displayed in the Copilot chat\'s input field","Copilot_StopGeneratingResponse":"OK, I stopped working on that request","_Copilot_StopGeneratingResponse.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-Copilot] Text displayed in the chat when user requests Copilot to stop generating a response","Copilot_ChatHistoryHydrationFailed":"If this is a continuation of an earlier chat and you want chat history, try closing and reopening the pane.","_Copilot_ChatHistoryHydrationFailed.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-Copilot] Text displayed in the chat when chat history fails to load","Copilot_RAIErrorResponse":"I\'m not able to do that. What else can I do for you?","_Copilot_RAIErrorResponse.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-Copilot] Text displayed in the chat when Copilot cannot generate a response due to Responsible AI guidelines","Copilot_GenericErrorResponse":"Sorry, something went wrong. I\'m working on it.","_Copilot_GenericErrorResponse.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-Copilot] Text displayed in the chat when Copilot encounters an error","Copilot_SearchPlanLoading":"I\'ll look for {0}...","_Copilot_SearchPlanLoading.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-Copilot] Text displayed in the chat when Copilot is searching for a user\'s request. {0} will be replaced with the user\'s request","Copilot_SearchPlanNoQueryLoading":"Looking for...","_Copilot_SearchPlanNoQueryLoading.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-Copilot] Text displayed in the chat when Copilot is searching for a user\'s request","Copilot_RAIError":"I\'m not able to do that. What else can I do for you?","_Copilot_RAIError.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-Copilot] Text displayed in the chat when Copilot cannot generate a response due to Responsible AI guidelines","Copilot_TimeoutError":"I can\'t process your request right now. Try again in a little while.","_Copilot_TimeoutError.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-Copilot] Text displayed in the chat when Copilot times out.","Copilot_ThrottlingError":"You\'ve reached the limit on the number of requests per hour. Try again in a little while.","_Copilot_ThrottlingError.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-Copilot] Text displayed in the chat when user maxes out their number of requests per hour.","Copilot_LicenseError":"Your account doesn\'t have the right license to use Copilot. Contact your organization\'s admin to get started. If you just got a license, leave the app and then come back to see if that fixes things.","_Copilot_LicenseError.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-Copilot] Text displayed in the chat when user accesses Copilot without the right licensing.","Copilot_OdslProgramFailedResponse":"Sorry, I can\'t do that right now. Try again or select a suggestion.","_Copilot_OdslProgramFailedResponse.comment":"[TAG:APPS-ProjectWeb-Copilot] An error response from Copilot displayed in the Copilot chat pane when there is a runtime error while trying to execute a user-generated command","Copilot_OffensiveInputError":"Sorry, I can\'t work with that. Try making a new request.","_Copilot_OffensiveInputError.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-Copilot] Text displayed in the chat when user sends an offensive or inappropriate query.","Copilot_OffensiveOutputError":"Sorry, I can\'t generate content for this. Try making a new request.","_Copilot_OffensiveOutputError.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-Copilot] Text displayed in the chat when Copilot receives an offensive or inappropriate response from Sydney.","Copilot_UnsupportedProgram":"I can\'t do that just yet. Is there anything else I can do for you?","_Copilot_UnsupportedProgram.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-Copilot] Text displayed in the chat when Copilot receives a query for an unimplemented skill.","Copilot_RequestTooLargeError":"I can\'t process that much information at once. Try again with a shorter request.","_Copilot_RequestTooLargeError.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-Copilot] Text displayed in the chat when the user sends too large of a query.","Copilot_UnsupportedLanguageError":"I\'m still working to support other languages. For now, please try your request again in English.","_Copilot_UnsupportedLanguageError.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-Copilot] Text displayed in the chat when the user sends a query in a non-English language.","