r.","ICalendarDialog_DeprecationHeadsUp":"Heads-up!","_ICalendarDialog_DeprecationHeadsUp.comment":"[BRANDING][TAG:APPS-Planner-ICalendarDialog]Bold attention-grabbing text for deprecation warning.","ICalendarDialog_DeprecationSubtext":"The \\"Add plan to Outlook\\" with iCalendar feed feature will be retired starting on {0}. Make sure to update your workflows so everything keeps running smoothly.","_ICalendarDialog_DeprecationSubtext.comment":"{PlaceHolder=\\"iCalendar\\"}[BRANDING][TAG:APPS-Planner-ICalendarDialog]Deprecation warning message for iCalendar feature retirement. {0} will be replaced with the formatted retirement date.","ICalendarDialog_PublishAssignedTasksToCalenderHeader":"Add your \\"Assigned to me\\" tasks to Outlook calendar with an iCalendar feed","_ICalendarDialog_PublishAssignedTasksToCalenderHeader.comment":"[BRANDING][TAG:APPS-Planner-ICalendarDialog]Text for publish user tasks dialog header.","ICalendarDialog_PublishAssignedTasksToCalenderSubtitle":"You can make tasks that are assigned to you available in your Outlook calendar by publishing them to an iCalendar feed.","_ICalendarDialog_PublishAssignedTasksToCalenderSubtitle.comment":"[BRANDING][TAG:APPS-Planner-ICalendarDialog]Text for publish user tasks dialog subheader.","ICalendarDialog_Unpublish":"Don\'t publish, keep private","_ICalendarDialog_Unpublish.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-ICalendarDialog]Text for unpublish tasks option.","ICalendarDialog_UnpublishInfoForPlan":"Tasks won\'t appear on your Outlook calendar, and task information for your plan won\'t be shared.","_ICalendarDialog_UnpublishInfoForPlan.comment":"[BRANDING][TAG:APPS-Planner-ICalendarDialog]Info text for unpublish plan tasks option.","ICalendarDialog_UnpublishUserTasksInfo":"Tasks won\'t appear on your Outlook calendar, and task information will stay private in \\"Assigned to me\\".","_ICalendarDialog_UnpublishUserTasksInfo.comment":"[BRANDING][TAG:APPS-Planner-ICalendarDialog]Info text for unpublish user tasks option.