itle.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-LandingPage] Title for the Planner landing page","DeletePortfolioConfirmationDialog_Title":"Delete \'{0}\'?","_DeletePortfolioConfirmationDialog_Title.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-DeletePortfolioConfirmationDialog] Title for the delete portfolio dialog, {0} will be replaced with the portfolio name that is being deleted","DeletePortfolioConfirmationDialog_Description":"Connected plans will not be deleted, just disconnected. Any information you\'ve added to this portfolio will be deleted.","_DeletePortfolioConfirmationDialog_Description.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-DeletePortfolioConfirmationDialog] Description for the delete portfolio dialog","DeletePortfolioConfirmationDialog_DeleteButton":"Delete","_DeletePortfolioConfirmationDialog_DeleteButton.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-DeletePortfolioConfirmationDialog] Label for the delete button in the delete portfolio dialog","DeletePortfolioConfirmationDialog_CancelButton":"Cancel","_DeletePortfolioConfirmationDialog_CancelButton.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-DeletePortfolioConfirmationDialog] Label for the cancel button in the delete portfolio dialog","DeletePortfolioInProgressModal_Title":"Deleting portfolio","_DeletePortfolioInProgressModal_Title.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-DeletePortfolioInProgressModal] Title for the delete portfolio in progress modal","DeletePortfolioInProgressModal_Description":"This may take a moment. Stay in planner until deletion is completed.","_DeletePortfolioInProgressModal_Description.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-DeletePortfolioInProgressModal] Description for the delete portfolio in progress modal","DeletePortfolioFailedModal_Title":"Something went wrong","_DeletePortfolioFailedModal_Title.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-DeletePortfolioFailedModal] Title for the delete portfolio failed modal","DeletePortfolioFailedModal_Description":"We were unable to delete your portfolio","_DeletePortfolioFailedModal_Description.comment":"[TAG:APPS-Planner-DeletePortfolioFailedModal]